All Regions\\n\\n Argentina\\n\\n Australia\\n\\n Austria\\n\\n Belgium (fr)\\n\\n Belgium (nl)\\n\\n Brazil\\n\\n Bulgaria\\n\\n Canada (en)\\n\\n Canada (fr)\\n\\n Catalonia\\n\\n Chile\\n\\n China\\n\\n Colombia\\n\\n Croatia\\n\\n Czech Republic\\n\\n Denmark\\n\\n Estonia\\n\\n Finland\\n\\n France\\n\\n Germany\\n\\n Greece\\n\\n Hong Kong\\n\\n Hungary\\n\\n Iceland\\n\\n India (en)\\n\\n Indonesia (en)\\n\\n Ireland\\n\\n Israel (en)\\n\\n Italy\\n\\n Japan\\n\\n Korea\\n\\n Latvia\\n\\n Lithuania\\n\\n Malaysia (en)\\n\\n Mexico\\n\\n Netherlands\\n\\n New Zealand\\n\\n Norway\\n\\n Pakistan (en)\\n\\n Peru\\n\\n Philippines (en)\\n\\n Poland\\n\\n Portugal\\n\\n Romania\\n\\n Russia\\n\\n Saudi Arabia\\n\\n Singapore\\n\\n Slovakia\\n\\n Slovenia\\n\\n South Africa\\n\\n Spain (ca)\\n\\n Spain (es)\\n\\n Sweden\\n\\n Switzerland (de)\\n\\n Switzerland (fr)\\n\\n Taiwan\\n\\n Thailand (en)\\n\\n Turkey\\n\\n US (English)\\n\\n US (Spanish)\\n\\n Ukraine\\n\\n United Kingdom\\n\\n Vietnam (en)\\n\\n Any Time\\n\\n Past Day\\n\\n Past Week\\n\\n Past Month\\n\\n Past Year\\n\\n## [Regional Transfer Stations - Miami-Dade County](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamidade.gov%2Fglobal%2Fservice.page%3FMduid_service%3Dser1464808248005568&rut=88208de39df6b15e1465b4b1f58abb034ea67797ae2c4630fcb8baa0b3eeb78b)\\n\\n //duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamidade.gov%2Fglobal%2Fservice.page%3FMduid_service%3Dser1464808248005568&rut=88208de39df6b15e1465b4b1f58abb034ea67797ae2c4630fcb8baa0b3eeb78b\\n\\n [www.miamidade.gov/global/service.page?Mduid_service=ser1464808248005568](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamidade.gov%2Fglobal%2Fservice.page%3FMduid_service%3Dser1464808248005568&rut=88208de39df6b15e1465b4b1f58abb034ea67797ae2c4630fcb8baa0b3eeb78b)\\n\\n [Most garbage and trash collected by county, municipal and private waste haulers is delivered to one of 3 regional transfer stations in Miami-Dade County. This distribution system helps reduce truck traffic on roads, travel time for waste haulers and reduce fuel consumption by eliminating multiple trips to remote disposal sites.](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamidade.gov%2Fglobal%2Fservice.page%3FMduid_service%3Dser1464808248005568&rut=88208de39df6b15e1465b4b1f58abb034ea67797ae2c4630fcb8baa0b3eeb78b)\\n\\n## [Miami-Dade Central Transfer Station - Lanfill Near Me](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fnearestlandfill.com%2Forg%2Fmiami%2Ddade%2Dcentral%2Dtransfer%2Dstation%2F&rut=b7e79054760fdab4cd3459426133f30a98b5ef5edbedd2160fcb2115984e012c)\\n\\n //duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fnearestlandfill.com%2Forg%2Fmiami%2Ddade%2Dcentral%2Dtransfer%2Dstation%2F&rut=b7e79054760fdab4cd3459426133f30a98b5ef5edbedd2160fcb2115984e012c\\n\\n [nearestlandfill.com/org/miami-dade-central-transfer-station/](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fnearestlandfill.com%2Forg%2Fmiami%2Ddade%2Dcentral%2Dtransfer%2Dstation%2F&rut=b7e79054760fdab4cd3459426133f30a98b5ef5edbedd2160fcb2115984e012c)\\n\\n [Miami-Dade Central Transfer Station : recycling center, hazardous waste, prices and rates, free dump day, customer service. ★★★ Visitors reviews.](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fnearestlandfill.com%2Forg%2Fmiami%2Ddade%2Dcentral%2Dtransfer%2Dstation%2F&rut=b7e79054760fdab4cd3459426133f30a98b5ef5edbedd2160fcb2115984e012c)\\n\\n## [Disposal Sites - Hialeah, FL](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hialeahfl.gov%2F973%2FDisposal%2DSites&rut=40def425f786d2e28106df024b2fa0b4451b646bd81da4f22972d3e0ff39d3d1)\\n\\n //duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hialeahfl.gov%2F973%2FDisposal%2DSites&rut=40def425f786d2e28106df024b2fa0b4451b646bd81da4f22972d3e0ff39d3d1\\n\\n [www.hialeahfl.gov/973/Disposal-Sites](//duckduckgo.com/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hialeahfl.gov%2F973%2FDisposal%2DSites&rut=40def425f786d2e28106df024b2fa0b4451b646bd81da4f22972d3e0ff39d3d1)\\n\\n [Locations for Disposal of Construction Debris and Home Chemicals: Miami Dade County Nort