{"type":"message","id":"caaef84a","parentId":"84beb1d2","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:37:40.038Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A4B5BD8C3F31F3DEDEF\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"18185109688321@lid\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"120363425630314527@g.us\",\n  \"sender\": \"Alex Naranjo\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Master Agent\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Alex Naranjo (+13059152810)\",\n  \"id\": \"18185109688321@lid\",\n  \"name\": \"Alex Naranjo\",\n  \"e164\": \"+13059152810\"\n}\n```\n\nOk great Jose is in this chat and you will now serve as his personal assistant."}],"timestamp":1773617860037}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ecf85a8","parentId":"caaef84a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T23:37:45.354Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThanks Alex! Just to be clear — Jose is already my primary user and the one who set me up 👑\n\nI'm happy to help *both* of you in this group chat. Jose is the boss, and I'll assist anyone here who needs something.\n\nJose, Alex — just tag me with whatever you need anytime. I'm always on 💪"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":81,"cacheRead":38528,"cacheWrite":1039,"totalTokens":39651,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773617860038}}
