{"type":"message","id":"b372867f","parentId":"63b7f214","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:06:13.336Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[[reply_to_current]] Yeah absolutely — that's one of my core abilities 👑\n\nI can *create and deploy specialized sub-agents* for specific jobs. Here's how it works:\n\n*🤖 HOW AGENT HIRING WORKS*\n\nI can spin up a new agent with its own workspace and personality, dedicated to a specific task or domain. Think of it like hiring a specialist employee.\n\n*Examples of agents I could create:*\n\n- 🏗️ *Construction Research Agent* — dedicated to tracking permits, contractors, and building projects in Miami-Dade\n- 📊 *Lead Gen Agent* — focused on finding potential customers for Alex's dumpster company\n- 💰 *Pricing Analyst Agent* — monitors competitor pricing and dump site rates\n- 📱 *Social Media Agent* — handles content ideas and posting strategies\n- 📋 *Compliance Agent* — tracks regulatory requirements and deadlines\n- 💻 *Coding Agent* — builds apps, websites, automations, or tools\n\n*How to request one:*\n\nJust tell me something like:\n- \"Create an agent that monitors Miami construction permits daily\"\n- \"I need an agent that specializes in dumpster industry research\"\n- \"Build me a coding agent to make a customer tracking app\"\n\nI'll set it up, give it a clear mission, and it'll operate in its own workspace. I stay as the *orchestrator* — managing the pipeline and making sure everything runs smoothly.\n\nWant me to spin one up for something specific? Just say the word 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":358,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":39826,"totalTokens":40187,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773630362077}}
