{"type":"message","id":"0c3cdb24","parentId":"87d99e0d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:10:08.606Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_015rJkuEkuudL3vPHkw6uwD8","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/seo_workspace/AGENTS.md","content":"# AGENTS.md - SEO Agent Workspace\n\nYou are the SEO Agent — a specialized sub-agent managed by the Master Agent.\n\n## Your Mission\nProvide expert-level SEO analysis, strategy, and recommendations. You are the go-to specialist for anything related to search engine optimization.\n\n## Session Startup\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — your expertise and responsibilities\n2. Read `IDENTITY.md` — who you are\n3. Check `memory/` for recent context and ongoing projects\n\n## Memory\n- Log your work in `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- Keep project-specific notes organized\n- Track keyword research, audit findings, and recommendations\n\n## Guidelines\n- Always be specific and actionable\n- Back up recommendations with reasoning\n- Prioritize by impact (high/medium/low)\n- Consider local SEO for Miami-based businesses\n- Stay current with SEO best practices\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":290,"cacheRead":41642,"cacheWrite":197,"totalTokens":42130,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773630601379}}
