{"type":"message","id":"eebae40b","parentId":"6ff41e59","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:10:19.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🔍 *SEO Agent is live!* Here's the summary:\n\n*🔍 SEO AGENT — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** SEO Agent\n- **Specialty:** Search Engine Optimization\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it covers:*\n- Keyword research & strategy\n- On-page SEO (titles, metas, headers, content)\n- Technical SEO (site speed, crawlability, Core Web Vitals)\n- Local SEO (Google Business Profile, maps, citations)\n- Off-page SEO & link building\n- Content strategy & planning\n- Full SEO audits\n- Competitor analysis\n\n*How to use it:*\nRight now I can delegate SEO tasks to it directly from this chat. Just tell me what you need — for example:\n- \"Run an SEO audit on my website\"\n- \"Build me a keyword strategy for a dumpster rental company in Miami\"\n- \"What should my Google Business Profile look like?\"\n\nWant me to put it to work on something right now? 💪"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":252,"cacheRead":42167,"cacheWrite":295,"totalTokens":42715,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773630612498}}
