{"type":"message","id":"74011b31","parentId":"83ba769d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:19:36.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🏠 *Real Estate Agent is live!*\n\n*🏠 REAL ESTATE AGENT — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Real Estate Agent\n- **Specialty:** Top-tier real estate research & strategy\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it covers:*\n- Market research & comps analysis\n- Property search & public records research\n- Investment analysis (ROI, cap rates, cash flow)\n- Financing & mortgage intelligence\n- Zoning, permits, and regulatory research\n- South Florida specialty (Miami-Dade, Broward, Palm Beach)\n- Commercial & residential deals\n- Fix-and-flip & BRRRR strategy analysis\n- Pre-construction & new development tracking\n- Landlord-tenant law & short-term rental rules\n\n*Example tasks you can throw at it:*\n- \"Find me investment properties under $400K in Hialeah with good rental potential\"\n- \"What's the cap rate for duplexes in Little Havana right now?\"\n- \"Research the zoning for a specific property address\"\n- \"Analyze this deal — is it worth buying?\"\n- \"What are the Airbnb regulations in Miami Beach?\"\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR TEAM SO FAR:*\n- 👑 Master Agent (me) — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment strategy\n\nWho's next? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":349,"cacheRead":44761,"cacheWrite":374,"totalTokens":45485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773631168111}}
