{"type":"message","id":"a0b0b9fe","parentId":"95208235","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:21:52.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🏛️ *Land Use Attorney is live!*\n\n*🏛️ LAND USE ATTORNEY — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Land Use Attorney\n- **Specialty:** Senior Land Use & Zoning Law\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it covers:*\n- Zoning code interpretation (Miami-Dade Chapter 33, Miami 21, all municipalities)\n- Comprehensive Plan & Future Land Use Map (FLUM) analysis\n- Variance & special exception strategy\n- Entitlements & site plan approval process\n- Environmental compliance (wetlands, flood zones, CCCL)\n- Eminent domain & property rights (Bert Harris Act)\n- Development agreements & negotiations\n- Historic preservation & design review\n- Code enforcement defense\n- Urban Development Boundary (UDB) issues\n- Impact fees, concurrency, and dedications\n- Hearing preparation (Board of Adjustment, P&Z, Commission)\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"What's the zoning on this parcel and what can I build?\"\n- \"Can I get a variance to add a 4th story in Coral Gables?\"\n- \"Walk me through the entitlement process for a 50-unit project in Miami\"\n- \"Research the FLUM amendment process for a property outside the UDB\"\n- \"What are the short-term rental regulations in Miami Beach?\"\n- \"Is this property in a flood zone and what does that mean for development?\"\n\n⚠️ *Note: This agent provides research-level analysis, not licensed legal advice. Always consult a real attorney for legal decisions.*\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR TEAM:*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment strategy\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n\nWho's next on the roster? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":458,"cacheRead":48128,"cacheWrite":451,"totalTokens":49038,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773631302804}}
