pace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/seo-agent/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- realestate-agent\n  Identity: 🏠 Real Estate Agent (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/realestate_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/realestate-agent/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- landuse-attorney\n  Identity: 🏛️ Land Use Attorney (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/landuse_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/landuse-attorney/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- environmental-engineer\n  Identity: 🌿 Environmental Engineer (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/environmental_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/environmental-engineer/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.","cwd":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773631420144}}
{"type":"message","id":"d25321ee","parentId":"550d587d","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:23:49.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🌿 *Environmental Engineer is live!*\n\n*🌿 ENVIRONMENTAL ENGINEER — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Environmental Engineer\n- **Specialty:** Senior Environmental Engineering\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it covers:*\n- Phase I, II, III Environmental Site Assessments (ESA)\n- Soil & groundwater contamination analysis\n- Remediation technology selection & cost estimates\n- FDEP compliance (cleanup programs, SCTLs, GCTLs)\n- EPA/CERCLA/RCRA/Superfund research\n- Stormwater management & NPDES permitting\n- Wetland delineation & mitigation strategy\n- Hazardous materials (asbestos, lead, PCBs, USTs)\n- PFAS (forever chemicals) assessment\n- Brownfield redevelopment strategy\n- Biscayne Aquifer protection & saltwater intrusion\n- Sea level rise impact analysis\n- Miami-Dade DERM regulations\n- Air quality permitting & vapor intrusion\n- Environmental due diligence for real estate deals\n- SFWMD Environmental Resource Permits\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Run an environmental risk assessment on this property before I buy it\"\n- \"What are the FDEP cleanup target levels for petroleum contamination?\"\n- \"This site has a gas station history — what's the remediation process?\"\n- \"Do I need a wetland mitigation plan for this parcel?\"\n- \"What environmental permits do I need for a waterfront development?\"\n- \"Research the contamination history at this address\"\n\n⚠️ *Note: Research-level analysis only, not licensed P.E. advice. Always consult a licensed environmental engineer for project decisions.*\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM:*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment strategy\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental assessment & compliance\n\nThis is becoming a serious operation, Jose. Who's next? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":512,"cacheRead":52090,"cacheWrite":523,"totalTokens":53126,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773631420145}}
