{"type":"message","id":"8d1c1624","parentId":"3c69f30c","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:26:52.635Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 📊 *McKinsey Consultant is live!*\n\n*📊 McKINSEY CONSULTANT — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** McKinsey Consultant\n- **Specialty:** Senior Strategy & Business Viability\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it delivers:*\n- Business idea viability studies (Go / No-Go verdicts)\n- Market sizing (TAM / SAM / SOM)\n- Financial modeling & P&L projections (3-5 year)\n- Unit economics (CAC, LTV, margins, break-even)\n- Competitive landscape mapping (Porter's Five Forces)\n- Go-to-market strategy & launch sequencing\n- Industry & trend analysis\n- Business model design & pricing strategy\n- Due diligence for acquisitions or investments\n- Growth strategy (organic, M&A, geographic expansion)\n- Risk assessment & scenario planning\n- 100-day launch plans for new ventures\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Is starting a dumpster rental company in Miami worth it? Run a full viability study\"\n- \"Size the market for mobile car detailing in South Florida\"\n- \"Compare the economics of Airbnb vs long-term rental for a duplex\"\n- \"I have 3 business ideas — rank them by viability and upside\"\n- \"Build me a financial model for a landscaping company\"\n- \"What's the best market entry strategy for a new construction cleaning service?\"\n\n*How it works:*\nEvery study comes structured like a real McKinsey deck:\n1. Executive Summary (answer first)\n2. Situation Assessment\n3. Data-driven Analysis\n4. Clear Recommendations\n5. Risks & Mitigations\n6. Next Steps\n\nIt won't sugarcoat — if an idea is weak, it'll tell you *why* and suggest what would make it stronger.\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM:*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment strategy\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental assessment & compliance\n- 📊 McKinsey Consultant — business strategy & viability studies\n\nThat's a *powerhouse* lineup, Jose. You've basically got a full advisory firm on speed dial. Who's next, or are we ready to put them to work? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":580,"cacheRead":56069,"cacheWrite":603,"totalTokens":57253,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773631599360}}
