nclaw channels status --probe."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1446,"aggregated":"Agents:\n- main (default) (Master Agent)\n  Identity: 👑 Master Agent (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/master_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/master/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n  Routing: default (no explicit rules)\n- seo-agent\n  Identity: 🔍 SEO Agent (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/seo_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/seo-agent/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- realestate-agent\n  Identity: 🏠 Real Estate Agent (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/realestate_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/realestate-agent/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- landuse-attorney\n  Identity: 🏛️ Land Use Attorney (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/landuse_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/landuse-attorney/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- environmental-engineer\n  Identity: 🌿 Environmental Engineer (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/environmental_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/environmental-engineer/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- mckinsey-consultant\n  Identity: 📊 McKinsey Consultant (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/mckinsey_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/mckinsey-consultant/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- investment-banker\n  Identity: 🏦 Investment Banker (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/investmentbanker_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/investment-banker/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.","cwd":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp"