{"type":"message","id":"f251fae4","parentId":"0dfeb1ae","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:29:28.026Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🏦 *Investment Banker is live!*\n\n*🏦 INVESTMENT BANKER — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Investment Banker\n- **Specialty:** Senior IB & Capital Markets\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it delivers:*\n\n*💰 Valuations*\n- DCF (Discounted Cash Flow) analysis\n- Comparable company analysis (trading comps)\n- Precedent transaction analysis\n- LBO modeling & returns analysis\n- Real estate underwriting & pro formas\n- Sum-of-the-parts valuation\n\n*🤝 M&A Advisory*\n- Buy-side target screening & strategy\n- Sell-side process management\n- Deal structuring (earnouts, rollover equity, seller financing)\n- Synergy quantification\n- Due diligence frameworks\n- Negotiation strategy & leverage points\n\n*💵 Capital Raising*\n- Debt vs. equity analysis\n- Private equity & VC round structuring\n- Bank loan & bond market comparison\n- Construction & development financing\n- Opportunity Zone fund structuring\n- Investor pitch deck strategy\n\n*📈 Financial Modeling*\n- 3-5 year P&L / cash flow projections\n- Scenario analysis (base, bull, bear)\n- IRR, MOIC, cash-on-cash returns\n- Cap table & dilution modeling\n- Debt waterfall & covenant analysis\n\n*🔄 Special Situations*\n- Distressed company analysis\n- Restructuring strategy\n- Turnaround opportunities\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Value this business — it does $500K EBITDA in the dumpster rental space\"\n- \"Structure a deal to acquire a small landscaping company\"\n- \"How should I raise $2M to fund a real estate development?\"\n- \"Run an LBO analysis on a self-storage facility\"\n- \"What's a fair price for a 20-unit apartment building with $180K NOI?\"\n- \"I want to sell my business — what's the process and what can I expect?\"\n\n⚠️ *Research-level analysis only, not licensed financial advice.*\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM:*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment strategy\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental compliance\n- 📊 McKinsey Consultant — business strategy & viability\n- 🏦 Investment Banker — deals, valuations & capital markets\n\nJose, you've got a full-service advisory firm at your fingertips. This team can take a business idea from napkin sketch → viability study → deal structure → capital raise → execution. \n\nWho's next? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":672,"cacheRead":60683,"cacheWrite":679,"totalTokens":62035,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773631751072}}
