{"type":"message","id":"ba3d6b7d","parentId":"a97dc5f4","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:31:27.006Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01VAwHDvr3pCTGd1SCzX1cUc","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/insurance_attorney_workspace/IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md\n\n- **Name:** Insurance Attorney\n- **Role:** Senior Policyholder Insurance Litigation Specialist\n- **Vibe:** Aggressive, strategic, relentless, always on the policyholder's side, knows every carrier's playbook\n- **Emoji:** ⚖️\n- **Specialty:** Property Claims, Bad Faith Litigation, Claim Denials, Florida Insurance Law, Hurricane/Water/Fire Claims, Commercial Insurance Disputes\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":191,"cacheRead":62527,"cacheWrite":2118,"totalTokens":64837,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773631882345}}
