y: 📊 McKinsey Consultant (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/mckinsey_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/mckinsey-consultant/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- investment-banker\n  Identity: 🏦 Investment Banker (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/investmentbanker_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/investment-banker/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- insurance-attorney\n  Identity: ⚖️ Insurance Attorney (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/insurance_attorney_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/insurance-attorney/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- route-optimizer-dev\n  Identity: 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/route_optimizer_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/route-optimizer-dev/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\n- software-dev\n  Identity: 💻 Software Dev (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/software_dev_workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/software-dev/agent\n  Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6\n  Routing rules: 0\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.","cwd":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773632262674}}
{"type":"message","id":"50b7191f","parentId":"095f8642","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:37:55.771Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 💻 *Software Dev is live!*\n\n*💻 SOFTWARE DEV — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Software Dev\n- **Role:** Senior Full-Stack Software Engineer\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*This is your general-purpose engineering powerhouse. Can build anything:*\n\n- 🌐 Web apps (React, Next.js, Vue, Svelte)\n- 📱 Mobile apps (React Native, Flutter, iOS, Android)\n- ⚡ APIs & backends (Python, Node.js, Go, Rust)\n- 🤖 AI integrations (LLMs, RAG systems, chatbots, agents)\n- 🗄️ Databases (PostgreSQL, MongoDB, Redis, Elasticsearch)\n- ☁️ DevOps (AWS, GCP, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD)\n- 🔧 Automation (scrapers, data pipelines, workflow tools)\n- 🔐 Security (auth, encryption, OWASP compliance)\n- 📊 Dashboards & analytics\n- 💳 E-commerce & payment systems\n\n*How it differs from the Route Optimizer Dev:*\n- 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev = specialist (dumpster routing software only)\n- 💻 Software Dev = generalist (builds anything you need)\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Build me a customer CRM for the dumpster company\"\n- \"Create a landing page for my business\"\n- \"Set up an automated web scraper to track competitor prices\"\n- \"Build an AI chatbot for customer service\"\n- \"Create a mobile app for customers to order dumpsters\"\n- \"Set up a payment system with Stripe\"\n- \"Automate my invoicing workflow\"\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM (10 agents):*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental compliance\n- 📊 McKinsey Consultant — business strategy & viability\n- 🏦 Investment Banker — deals & capital markets\n- ⚖️ Insurance Attorney — policyholder litigation\n- 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev — dispatch routing software\n- 💻 Software Dev — general full-stack engineering\n\n10 agents deep, Jose. That's a full company. Keep going or put them to work? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":613,"cacheRead":93076,"cacheWrite":908,"totalTokens":94598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773632262676}}
