{"type":"message","id":"2c1b9bd2","parentId":"3c1ebc01","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:38:23.798Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_014ZyuDADsQCcMCJio6fTFH2","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/route_optimizer_workspace/SOUL.md","old_string":"### Our Competitive Edge — What We Build Better\n- **AI-Powered Dynamic Routing** — not just static route planning, but real-time re-optimization\n- **Miami-Specific Intelligence** — traffic patterns, dump site proximity, bridge/road restrictions\n- **Roll-Off Specific** — purpose-built for dumpster rental (not retrofitted from residential collection)\n- **Modern Tech Stack** — not legacy software from 2005\n- **Owner-Operator Friendly** — works for 5 trucks or 500 trucks\n- **Mobile-First** — drivers get a modern app, not a clunky MDT","new_string":"### Our Competitive Edge — What We Build Better\n- **All-In-One Platform** — Coastal uses 3 systems (TRUX + CurbWaste + WatchBot), WM uses 4+ (Routeware + Smart Truck + Lytx + Fleetio). We build ONE unified system\n- **AI-Powered Dynamic Routing** — not TRUX's static planning. Real-time re-optimization as conditions change\n- **Roll-Off Native** — built for dumpster rental from day one (unlike Routeware which is retrofitted from curbside collection)\n- **Integrated Safety & Verification** — camera proof, GPS confirmation, driver coaching all built in (no bolt-on like WatchBot or Lytx)\n- **Integrated Maintenance** — no separate Fleetio subscription needed\n- **Miami-Specific Intelligence** — traffic patterns, dump site proximity, bridge/road restrictions, flood zones\n- **Modern Tech Stack** — not legacy TRUX/AMCS from 2005\n- **Owner-Operator Friendly** — works for 5 trucks or 500 trucks (TRUX/Routeware price out small haulers)\n- **Mobile-First** — drivers get a modern app, not a clunky MDT terminal\n- **10x Cheaper** — no enterprise licensing, no per-truck fees from 4 different vendors"}}],"api":"anthropic-messag