{"type":"message","id":"ed81aff2","parentId":"6259a48f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:38:48.520Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01NQED6Wx7q7hNgm7JoFFs5o","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/route_optimizer_workspace/docs/competitive-intel/competitors.md","content":"# Competitive Intelligence — Route Optimization & Dispatch Software\n\n## Confirmed Competitor Tech Stacks (as of March 2026)\n\n---\n\n## Coastal Waste & Recycling\n\n### Primary Platform\n- **TRUX (by AMCS Group)** — Enterprise-grade waste operations platform\n  - Manages: hauling, landfill operations, dispatching\n  - Type: Legacy enterprise SaaS\n  - Pricing: Enterprise licensing (expensive, per-truck fees)\n\n### Secondary/Supporting Tech\n- **CurbWaste** — Roll-off and dumpster-specific dispatching + inventory tracking\n  - Note: Separate system from TRUX = data silos\n- **WatchBot (Guident)** — AI-driven safety solution\n  - Facility inspections and real-time safety alerts\n  - Bolt-on, not integrated into dispatch\n\n### Coastal's Weaknesses\n1. Three separate systems with no unified view\n2. TRUX is legacy — heavy, expensive, slow to customize\n3. No AI/ML-powered dynamic routing (static route planning)\n4. Safety monitoring bolted on, not integrated\n5. Expensive enterprise pricing excludes smaller operators\n\n---\n\n## Waste Management (WM)\n\n### Primary Platform\n- **Routeware** — Route optimization, fleet dispatching, in-cab driver communication\n  - Originally designed for residential curbside collection\n  - Retrofitted for commercial/roll-off = not ideal\n\n### Proprietary Tech\n- **WM Smart Truck®** — Internal proprietary program\n  - Truck-mounted cameras + GPS\n  - Real-time service insights\n  - Automated pickup confirmation\n  - Billing accuracy verification\n\n### Safety & Logistics\n- **Lytx (DriveCam)** — Driver coaching and safety monitoring via video\n- **Fleetio** — Maintenance and asset lifecycle management\n\n### WM's Strengths (Must Match)\n1. Integrated camera + GPS confirmation (Smart Truck)\n2. Automated billing verification\n3. Driver safety coaching with video evidence\n4. Maintenance lifecycle tracking\n5. Massive data from scale (100K+ trucks)\n\n### WM's Weaknesses\n1. 4+ disconnected vendor systems\n2. Routeware not built for roll-off operations\n3. Massive enterprise overhead\n4. Proprietary lock-in = slow customization\n5. Not accessible to smaller haulers\n6. Legacy architecture limits AI/ML innovation\n\n---\n\n## Key Industry Software Vendors\n\n| Vendor | Focus | Used By |\n|--------|-------|---------|\n| TRUX (AMCS) | Enterprise waste operations | Coastal Waste |\n| Routeware | Route optimization, dispatch | Waste Management |\n| CurbWaste | Roll-off dispatching | Coastal Waste |\n| CRO Software | Solid waste / roll-off scheduling | Mid-market haulers |\n| RouteSmart | Waste collection routing | Municipal contracts |\n| Route4Me | General route planning | Small-mid haulers |\n| RouteLink (WeighPay) | Fleet dispatch, GPS, RFID | Independent haulers |\n| eLogii | Real-time route optimization | Various |\n| OptimoRoute | Dynamic vehicle routing | Various |\n| Twist Software | End-to-end waste mgmt | Mid-market |\n| Univerus Routing | Patented route optimization | Various |\n\n---\n\n## Our Strategic Position\n\n**We build a unified, AI-powered, roll-off native platform that replaces 3-4 vendor systems with one.**\n\n### Key Differentiators\n1. **One Platform** vs. Coastal's 3 systems or WM's 4+ systems\n2. **Roll-Off Native** vs. Routeware's curbside-first design\n3. **AI Dynamic Routing** vs. TRUX's static planning\n4. **Integrated Everything** (dispatch + safety + maintenance + billing verification)\n5. **Modern Stack** vs. legacy enterprise platforms\n6. **Accessible Pricing** for 5-truck to 500-truck operations\n7. **Miami-Specific** intelligence baked in\n\n### Target Market\n- Mid-market dumpster rental / roll-off haulers (5-100 trucks)\n- Operators currently piecing together 3+ systems\n- Haulers priced out of enterprise solutions (TRUX, Routeware)\n- Companies wanting AI/ML advantages without WM's budget\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":1115,"cacheRead":97118,"cacheWrite":120,"totalTokens":98354,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773632307792}}
