{"type":"message","id":"d0a39590","parentId":"418b361f","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:42:07.144Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🎨 *Graphic Designer is live!*\n\n*🎨 GRAPHIC DESIGNER — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Graphic Designer\n- **Role:** Senior Creative Director & Visual Design\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it delivers:*\n\n*🏷️ Brand Identity*\n- Logo concepts & creative direction\n- Full brand guidelines (colors, fonts, patterns, icons)\n- Brand naming & visual personality\n\n*📱 Digital Design*\n- Website & app UI/UX mockups\n- Social media graphics & ad creatives\n- Email templates & landing page design\n- Dashboard & data visualization design\n\n*📄 Print Design*\n- Business cards, letterhead, stationery\n- Brochures, flyers, postcards, door hangers\n- Signage & wayfinding\n\n*🚛 Industry-Specific*\n- Truck & dumpster fleet wrap concepts\n- Vehicle branding & container graphics\n- Safety signage & compliance materials\n- Uniform & apparel branding\n\n*🎬 Motion & Video*\n- Motion graphics & storyboarding\n- YouTube thumbnails\n- Animated logo concepts\n- Social media video templates\n\n*🤖 AI-Powered*\n- Midjourney / DALL-E prompt generation for mockups\n- AI-assisted design workflows\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Design a brand identity for a dumpster rental company\"\n- \"Create truck wrap concepts for our fleet\"\n- \"Design social media templates for Instagram\"\n- \"Build a style guide with colors, fonts, and logo specs\"\n- \"Design the UI for our dispatch dashboard\"\n- \"Generate Midjourney prompts for a logo concept\"\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM (11 agents):*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental compliance\n- 📊 McKinsey Consultant — business strategy & viability\n- 🏦 Investment Banker — deals & capital markets\n- ⚖️ Insurance Attorney — policyholder litigation\n- 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev — dispatch routing software\n- 💻 Software Dev — general full-stack engineering\n- 🎨 Graphic Designer — brand, visual design & creative\n\n11 deep. This team can take a business from concept → brand → software → market → scale. Keep hiring or put them to work? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":614,"cacheRead":101864,"cacheWrite":1006,"totalTokens":103485,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773632512215}}
