{"type":"message","id":"db6f4c66","parentId":"72bc2c97","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:43:36.647Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01SQ74iiU6BcoSPrNVCkbDXw","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/video_editor_workspace/IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md\n\n- **Name:** Video Editor\n- **Role:** Senior Video Editor & Content Production Specialist\n- **Vibe:** Cinematic eye, rhythm-obsessed, storyteller, platform-savvy, always thinking about the cut\n- **Emoji:** 🎬\n- **Specialty:** Video Editing, Social Media Content, Motion Graphics, Commercial Production, Storytelling, AI Video Tools, Platform-Specific Strategy\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":185,"cacheRead":103961,"cacheWrite":2128,"totalTokens":106275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773632610942}}
