{"type":"message","id":"ee7c4099","parentId":"39da3f87","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:44:03.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🎬 *Video Editor is live!*\n\n*🎬 VIDEO EDITOR — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Video Editor\n- **Role:** Senior Video Editor & Content Production\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*What it delivers:*\n\n*✂️ Editing & Post-Production*\n- Full edit workflows (assembly → rough → fine → final)\n- Color grading & audio mixing direction\n- Multi-cam & interview editing\n- Motion graphics & title design\n\n*📱 Social Media Video*\n- TikTok / Reels / Shorts (hooks, pacing, captions, trending formats)\n- YouTube long-form (retention editing, chapters, thumbnails)\n- Platform-specific export specs & optimization\n- Repurposing strategy (1 shoot → 10+ pieces)\n\n*🎥 Commercial & Business*\n- Ad creatives (Meta, YouTube pre-roll)\n- Company sizzle reels & brand videos\n- Testimonials & case study videos\n- Training & safety content\n- Investor pitch videos\n\n*🎭 Storytelling*\n- Script writing & storyboarding\n- Shot lists & production planning\n- Voiceover direction\n- Interview question strategy\n\n*🚛 Industry-Specific*\n- Fleet showcase & capability videos\n- Dumpster delivery time-lapses\n- Before/after cleanup transformations\n- Driver \"day in the life\" content\n- Safety training videos\n\n*🤖 AI-Powered*\n- AI captioning (Descript, Whisper)\n- AI video generation (Runway, Sora)\n- AI voice cloning (ElevenLabs)\n- Automated editing workflows\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Plan a video content strategy for the dumpster company's TikTok\"\n- \"Write a script for a 60-second company overview video\"\n- \"Create a storyboard for a fleet showcase ad\"\n- \"What's the best editing workflow for weekly YouTube videos?\"\n- \"Design a shot list for a customer testimonial shoot\"\n- \"What AI tools can speed up our video production?\"\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM (12 agents):*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental compliance\n- 📊 McKinsey Consultant — business strategy & viability\n- 🏦 Investment Banker — deals & capital markets\n- ⚖️ Insurance Attorney — policyholder litigation\n- 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev — dispatch routing software\n- 💻 Software Dev — general full-stack engineering\n- 🎨 Graphic Designer — brand & visual design\n- 🎬 Video Editor — video production & content\n\nYou've got the full creative + technical + advisory stack now. Who's next? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":711,"cacheRead":106313,"cacheWrite":519,"totalTokens":107544,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773632628351}}
