{"type":"message","id":"9252140e","parentId":"0af2948b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:45:25.030Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"3A18F1C898A38D644F54\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"170170932797663@lid\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"120363425630314527@g.us\",\n  \"sender\": \"Jose\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Master Agent\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Jose (+13053002364)\",\n  \"id\": \"170170932797663@lid\",\n  \"name\": \"Jose\",\n  \"e164\": \"+13053002364\"\n}\n```\n\ni need to hire a senior fleet manager, that checks the uattend data, routes, samsara, maintenance records, maintenance alerts, etc"}],"timestamp":1773632725028}}
