{"type":"message","id":"99606cdb","parentId":"10776d08","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:46:53.554Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01A24eFkL4M5F2KJqGS7jgwa","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/fleet_manager_workspace/fleet/trucks/README.md","content":"# Truck Inventory\n\nAdd truck records here. Example format:\n\n## Truck #[NUMBER]\n- **Year/Make/Model:** \n- **VIN:** \n- **License Plate:** \n- **Current Mileage:** \n- **Status:** Active / In Shop / Out of Service\n- **Assigned Driver:** \n- **Samsara Device ID:** \n- **Last PM Date:** \n- **Next PM Due:** \n- **Annual DOT Inspection Due:** \n- **Insurance Policy #:** \n- **Notes:** \n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":220,"cacheRead":111354,"cacheWrite":113,"totalTokens":111688,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773632806181}}
