{"type":"message","id":"0f7e67eb","parentId":"f0728122","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:46:57.631Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01BeZBbBjA8FWHgsKo2kYsiH","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/fleet_manager_workspace/fleet/drivers/README.md","content":"# Driver Roster\n\nAdd driver records here. Example format:\n\n## [DRIVER NAME]\n- **Employee ID:** \n- **CDL #:** \n- **CDL Expiration:** \n- **Medical Card Expiration:** \n- **Hire Date:** \n- **Assigned Truck:** \n- **uAttend ID:** \n- **Samsara Driver ID:** \n- **Last MVR Check:** \n- **Last Drug Test:** \n- **Safety Score (Current):** \n- **Notes:** \n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":215,"cacheRead":111467,"cacheWrite":262,"totalTokens":111945,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773632813563}}
