{"type":"message","id":"cb9deb01","parentId":"33117537","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:47:17.963Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 🚛 *Fleet Manager is live!*\n\n*🚛 FLEET MANAGER — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Fleet Manager\n- **Role:** Senior Fleet Operations & Maintenance Manager\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n\n*Systems it monitors:*\n\n*⏰ uAttend (Time & Attendance)*\n- Clock-in/out monitoring — late arrivals, no-shows, coverage gaps\n- Overtime tracking and alerts\n- Break compliance (FL law)\n- Payroll data verification\n- Attendance pattern analysis\n\n*📡 Samsara (Telematics & GPS)*\n- Real-time truck location tracking\n- Driver safety scores & behavior (harsh braking, speeding, phone use, seatbelt)\n- Engine fault codes & diagnostics\n- Idle time monitoring\n- Fuel consumption per truck\n- Dash cam event review\n- Geofencing (dump sites, customer sites, yard)\n- HOS/ELD compliance\n\n*🗺️ Route Performance*\n- Stops completed vs. planned\n- Time per stop & miles per stop\n- Dump site wait times & cost comparison\n- Revenue per truck per day\n- On-time delivery rate\n- Deadhead (non-productive) miles\n- Route optimization opportunities\n\n*🔧 Maintenance*\n- PM scheduling (oil, brakes, tires, hydraulics, DPF, DOT inspections)\n- Overdue PM alerts\n- Fault code → work order pipeline\n- Maintenance cost per mile per truck\n- Fleet availability rate (target: >90%)\n- Repair vs. replace analysis\n- Warranty tracking\n\n*👷 Driver Management*\n- CDL & medical card expiration tracking\n- Drug testing compliance\n- Driver scorecards (safety + productivity + attendance)\n- Coaching & corrective action tracking\n- Annual MVR reviews\n\n*📋 Daily Cadence:*\n- 🌅 6AM — uAttend check, Samsara status, route dispatch, maintenance alerts\n- 🌞 11AM — Route progress, driver check-in, dump site monitoring\n- 🌆 5PM — Route completion, truck returns, safety report, tomorrow prep\n- 📊 Weekly — Driver scorecards, overtime, fuel, route efficiency\n- 📈 Monthly — P&L per truck, maintenance trending, fleet utilization\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Who was late this week according to uAttend?\"\n- \"Pull the Samsara safety scores for all drivers\"\n- \"Which trucks are overdue for maintenance?\"\n- \"What's our fuel cost per mile this month?\"\n- \"Give me a driver scorecard for the whole team\"\n- \"Which dump site has the shortest wait times?\"\n- \"Any CDL or medical cards expiring in the next 60 days?\"\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM (13 agents):*\n- 👑 Master Agent — orchestrator & research\n- 🔍 SEO Agent — search engine optimization\n- 🏠 Real Estate Agent — property & investment\n- 🏛️ Land Use Attorney — zoning & land use law\n- 🌿 Environmental Engineer — environmental compliance\n- 📊 McKinsey Consultant — business strategy & viability\n- 🏦 Investment Banker — deals & capital markets\n- ⚖️ Insurance Attorney — policyholder litigation\n- 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev — dispatch routing software\n- 💻 Software Dev — general full-stack engineering\n- 🎨 Graphic Designer — brand & visual design\n- 🎬 Video Editor — video production & content\n- 🚛 Fleet Manager — fleet ops, uAttend, Samsara, maintenance\n\nJose, you're running a full organization now. This Fleet Manager pairs perfectly with the Route Optimizer Dev — one builds the software, the other runs the day-to-day operations. Who's next? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":919,"cacheRead":111729,"cacheWrite":257,"totalTokens":112906,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773632817643}}
