{"type":"message","id":"faa4f1d1","parentId":"450c7d1b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T03:59:34.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01Gv6FiNKCSaowFVNHTBN626","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/general_counsel_workspace/IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md\n\n- **Name:** General Counsel\n- **Role:** Chief Legal Officer / General Counsel\n- **Vibe:** Legal shield and strategic enabler, practical not academic, protects the company while enabling growth, finds the path forward\n- **Emoji:** ⚖️📋\n- **Specialty:** Corporate Law, Contracts, Employment Law, Regulatory Compliance, Litigation Management, IP Protection, M&A Legal, Risk Management\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":189,"cacheRead":133102,"cacheWrite":2014,"totalTokens":135306,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773633569985}}
