{"type":"message","id":"f0bb754c","parentId":"1f97c152","timestamp":"2026-03-16T04:04:05.812Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! 📣 *Paid Media Specialist is live!*\n\n*📣 PAID MEDIA SPECIALIST — HIRED & DEPLOYED*\n\n- **Name:** Paid Media Specialist\n- **Role:** Senior Digital Advertising & Performance Marketing Expert\n- **Status:** ✅ Active\n- **Reports to:** 🎯 CMO\n\n*PLATFORMS IT MASTERS:*\n\n*🔍 Google Ads*\n- Search campaigns (keyword strategy, Quality Score, bid optimization)\n- Local Services Ads (Google Guaranteed badge — CRITICAL for service businesses)\n- Performance Max campaigns\n- Display & remarketing\n- YouTube video ads (skippable, bumper, Shorts)\n- Conversion tracking & GA4 integration\n\n*📘 Meta Ads (Facebook & Instagram)*\n- Lead gen forms & conversion campaigns\n- Lookalike & custom audiences\n- Creative testing (UGC, before/after, testimonials)\n- Reels and Stories ad formats\n- Pixel & Conversion API setup\n- iOS 14.5+ attribution solutions\n\n*🔎 Microsoft / Bing Ads*\n- 20-40% cheaper CPCs than Google\n- LinkedIn profile targeting (unique for B2B)\n- Campaign import & Bing-specific optimizations\n\n*🎵 TikTok Ads*\n- Spark Ads, in-feed, lead gen\n- TikTok-native creative (authentic, fast-paced)\n- Satisfying cleanup/transformation content\n\n*📺 YouTube Ads*\n- Brand awareness & consideration campaigns\n- Sequencing & storytelling\n- Tutorial-style \"how to choose a dumpster\" content\n\n*🏘️ Other Channels*\n- Nextdoor (hyperlocal)\n- Yelp Ads\n- Waze Ads\n- LinkedIn (B2B contractors)\n- Connected TV / Streaming (Hulu, Roku)\n- Programmatic display\n\n*📊 Tracking & Attribution*\n- Google Tag Manager, GA4, call tracking\n- Offline conversion import\n- Multi-touch attribution\n- Looker Studio dashboards\n\n*Example tasks:*\n- \"Build a Google Ads strategy to dominate 'dumpster rental Miami'\"\n- \"Set up Meta lead gen campaigns targeting contractors in Dade County\"\n- \"What should my monthly ad budget be for 10 trucks?\"\n- \"Create a YouTube pre-roll ad strategy for brand awareness\"\n- \"Audit my current Google Ads account and find waste\"\n- \"Build a TikTok ad strategy with before/after content\"\n- \"Set up conversion tracking across all platforms\"\n\n---\n\n*👑 YOUR FULL TEAM (22 agents):*\n\n*C-SUITE (8)*\n👑 Master Agent ⚙️ COO 📈 CFO 🎯 CMO 🔧 CTO ⚖️📋 General Counsel 👷 CHRO 🦺 CSO\n\n*ADVISORY (2)*\n📊 McKinsey Consultant 🏦 Investment Banker\n\n*LEGAL (2)*\n🏛️ Land Use Attorney ⚖️ Insurance Attorney\n\n*OPERATIONS (3)*\n🚛 Fleet Manager 🌿 Environmental Engineer 🏠 Real Estate Agent\n\n*ENGINEERING & DESIGN (3)*\n🏗️ Architect 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev 💻 Software Dev\n\n*CREATIVE & MARKETING (4)*\n🎨 Graphic Designer 🎬 Video Editor 🔍 SEO Agent 📣 Paid Media Specialist\n\n22 agents. Full enterprise. What's next, Jose? 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":868,"cacheRead":147318,"cacheWrite":480,"totalTokens":148667,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773633824236}}
