{"type":"message","id":"dbec3a1e","parentId":"54e16129","timestamp":"2026-03-17T20:59:42.904Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Outlining agent task execution**","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0fd7760a07c3c6e20069b9c0b87ee0819c8d33300731427e18\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpucC5rQqihmAvAynomUPMkCQkDS_x_pYIS0ztBLW7PQkwLCGJjvEGZx52HZIYG6gKM7CMQ0TDWdqwaypquywWkIX_k7qxpS3UeyeqBEcHy6A9divKa_m31E1WxNDReiSBmlPA8i6SbuKsKeVB_F3tEvWlphtOhDTNzWXgtzhf10uVKJLcu5P4yBGv9zxO57bXhleTSpNBoSeFk8xySFq_cthdYhhHfeYlUjl4tzS2y5YuK-efzjymFMI-2Sk1oGEQ7P0JAEWGzQ_qcjZFW0Hsgr2QYj6rMkd3cJFbmmZmWRkLoEQgs0c8qV8s4mLPrqmZzw_gMDQOt1E8Y6hG4ngBVTKLVoi97w_uF9BetjfEYNs9y7f1RABKBk0dkfCL-2cMJYCmmDWVpivwDe_EKSyI42RVW0hQjWIoyjfkrs5OpcSjm_syvG7oDL9sbtqro7tJh_mkhx6p55cXOA4p3_wbpihjkebzMFweBoTW2IrQ_SHK4p2zMG0QQfU7z6Vy-4ZTWnAoiuWoIYaK1MhYa5cPL8VK5hOCyA2cfZvTILv6zmn6iR-kXzbNGtzFmazQIpAWQ0vGirGwMcc0UcirCk-xZC9teRp9-JRW4okkzvUuTKkM8p2e2pFr0NtpYNGcXYsOnnm-VM831NjX46DYIJrM2CIt-z7fIfk0N6ckGHF6AkDD3MVYFUAGhv1Ar80p7aSdSuH8PHznfSZSoEtXV-X1RaLBOAoxl5kGEWNkFeJg86_26AoVoJaXtx_kLN3BtSMqrY12zrFM7UcRrazu-NZsryT951QfSi5WuLrGpghshL6FlpapL7qTV6gTeK4Q1O1GIHuwEhMisiPM5ZwfBnsG8jvqg3t_wbDOhIvdmKW14yS4zmjZSwt6iaAe_aihIqIl_fynVTKCcV66ncSNb4zZcp8XF_ok2imSYrWJbnEla2OAzFY3zeL_YcMXFuxb5XufbxZ56ZyDSBfEZbk52Vx32yDcW0T07cDG2GDcNcDx5uYyOGM=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Outlining agent task execution**\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] By “execute” I mean putting those recommendations into action with the specialist agents you already hired. For this GBP + SEO + PMax project, the work would break down like this:\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 SEO Agent would:\n1. **Audit the current Google Business Profile** (categories, services, description, photos, posts, Q&A, reviews).\n2. **Fix GBP gaps** (add services/products, write SEO-rich description, seed Q&A, build posting calendar, plan review request cadence).\n3. **Audit citation consistency** (Yelp, Bing, BBB, Angi, etc.) and fix NAP issues.\n4. **Map GBP keywords** to on-site pages — create or tune service pages, city pages, FAQ schema, embed GBP map.\n5. **Package all GBP copy/assets** so you can update the profile quickly.\n\n### 📣 Paid Media Specialist would:\n1. **Link GBP to Google Ads** and pull in GBP conversion data.\n2. **Rebuild Performance Max asset groups** around the key service pillars (residential cleanout, construction, recycling, branded).\n3. **Update creative assets** (headlines, descriptions, callouts, image/video assets) using GBP photos + new social content.\n4. **Tune bidding strategy** (Target CPA → Target ROAS once data flows) and budget allocation.\n5. **Set up conversion tracking** for GBP calls/directions and import into Google Ads.\n\n### 📱 Social Media + Customer Service would:\n- Push review requests, publish GBP posts, respond to GBP Q&A and reviews within 24h, keeping signals fresh for local rank.\n\n---\n\nSo “execute” = I coordinate those agents to actually do the audit, write the copy, produce the assets, rebuild the campaigns, and hand you a done-for-you package (or even update things directly if you want). Let me know if you want me to spin up SEO + Paid Media for the audit/implementation.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0fd7760a07c3c6e20069b9c0b96d78819c9402a04d28c0e0e7\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.1-codex","usage":{"input":141587,"output":434,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142021,"cost":{"input":0.17698375000000002,"output":0.00434,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.18132375000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773781164750}}
