{"type":"message","id":"a95f3732","parentId":"6093ddae","timestamp":"2026-03-17T21:08:17.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have a full picture. Let me build the complete audit + checklists and save them as a document your team can work from."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01U14JeAydPbzjbAiGG6RedG","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace/audits/usa-dumpster-gbp-seo-pmax-audit.md","content":"# USA Dumpster & Recycling — Full Audit & Implementation Checklist\n## Google Business Profile + SEO + Performance Max\n### Date: March 17, 2026\n### Prepared by: Master Agent (👑) + SEO Agent (🔍) + Paid Media Specialist (📣)\n\n---\n\n⚠️ **THIS IS AN AUDIT + CHECKLIST ONLY. No changes will be made by agents. Your human team should execute each item manually.**\n\n---\n\n## PART 1: GOOGLE BUSINESS PROFILE (GBP) AUDIT\n\n### 📍 Current Profile Info Found\n- **Business Name:** USA Dumpster Rentals (also appears as \"USA Dumpster and Recycling\" on some directories)\n- **Address:** 3147 NW North River Dr, Miami, FL 33142, Suite #2\n- **Website:** usadumpsterrentals.net\n- **Secondary domain:** usascrapmetalcompany.com/dumpster-rental-miami/ (linked from main site)\n- **Service Area:** Miami-Dade County + Broward County (40-mile radius)\n- **Services:** 10, 20, 30, 40 yard roll-off dumpster rental, same-day delivery\n- **Reviews visible on site:** Multiple 5-star reviews with owner responses\n\n---\n\n### ✅ GBP OPTIMIZATION CHECKLIST\n\n#### A. Business Information (Check in GBP Manager)\n- [ ] **Primary Category:** Verify it's set to \"Dumpster Rental Service\" (NOT \"Waste Management Service\" as primary)\n- [ ] **Secondary Categories:** Add ALL that apply:\n  - Waste Management Service\n  - Recycling Center\n  - Roll Off Dumpster Service (if available)\n  - Junk Removal Service\n  - Construction Company (if doing C&D recycling)\n- [ ] **Business Name:** Ensure it matches EXACTLY across GBP, website, and all directories. Pick ONE: either \"USA Dumpster Rentals\" or \"USA Dumpster and Recycling\" — consistency is critical\n- [ ] **Address:** Verify Suite #2 is included and matches website footer exactly\n- [ ] **Phone Number:** Verify primary phone matches website. Use a LOCAL Miami number (305 or 786 area code), not toll-free\n- [ ] **Website URL:** Should link to usadumpsterrentals.net (verify this is the one set in GBP)\n- [ ] **Hours:** Verify all hours are set. Add special hours for holidays. If you offer after-hours/emergency, add that\n- [ ] **Service Area:** Log into GBP → Edit → Service Area → Add every city individually:\n  - Miami-Dade: Miami, Aventura, Cutler Bay, Doral, Hialeah, Miami Gardens, Miami Shores, Miami Springs, Hialeah Gardens, North Bay Village, North Miami, Pinecrest, Coral Gables, South Miami, Sunny Isles, El Portal, Miami Beach, Surfside, Sweetwater, West Miami, Opa-locka\n  - Broward: Hallandale, Lauderhill, Fort Lauderdale, Sunrise, Lauderdale Lakes, Pembroke Pines, North Lauderdale, Pompano Beach, Margate, Coconut Creek, Parkland, Coral Springs, Weston, Plantation, Tamarac, Cooper City, Davie, Miramar, Hollywood, Deerfield Beach, Oakland Park, Dania Beach\n- [ ] **Booking/Appointment URL:** Add a direct link to your contact/booking page\n\n#### B. Business Description (750 characters max)\n- [ ] **Rewrite the GBP description** to include target keywords naturally. Suggested template:\n\n> \"USA Dumpster Rentals provides fast, same-day roll-off dumpster rental service in Miami, FL and surrounding areas in Miami-Dade and Broward County. We offer 10, 20, 30, and 40 yard dumpsters for residential cleanouts, construction debris removal, demolition projects, commercial waste, and junk removal. Serving contractors, homeowners, property managers, and businesses with reliable delivery, affordable pricing, and professional service. Licensed and insured. Call now for a free quote — same-day delivery available 7 days a week.\"\n\n#### C. Services / Products Tab\n- [ ] Add each service individually in GBP Products/Services:\n  - **10 Yard Dumpster Rental** — description + price range\n  - **20 Yard Dumpster Rental** — description + price range\n  - **30 Yard Dumpster Rental** — description + price range\n  - **40 Yard Dumpster Rental** — description + price range\n  - **Same-Day Dumpster Delivery** — description\n  - **Construction Debris Removal** — description\n  - **Residential Cleanout Dumpsters** — description\n  - **Commercial Waste Services** — description\n  - **Junk Removal Services** — description\n  - **Scrap Metal Recycling** (if offered via USA Scrap Metal)\n- [ ] Include keywords in each service description (e.g., \"dumpster rental Miami\", \"roll-off dumpster near me\")\n- [ ] Add pricing or price ranges where possible (transparency boosts clicks)\n\n#### D. Photos & Videos\n- [ ] **Target: 100+ photos minimum** (check current count in GBP)\n- [ ] Upload categories:\n  - [ ] Fleet photos (each truck, branded, clean, professional)\n  - [ ] Each dumpster size (10, 20, 30, 40 yard — empty and on-site)\n  - [ ] Before/after cleanup photos (minimum 20 pairs)\n  - [ ] Team/driver photos (builds trust)\n  - [ ] Office/yard facility photos\n  - [ ] Delivery action shots (truck dropping dumpster)\n  - [ ] Job site photos (residential, commercial, construction)\n  - [ ] Logo and branding images\n- [ ] Upload at least 3-5 short videos:\n  - Dumpster delivery time-lapse\n  - Before/after cleanup transformation\n  - Team introduction\n  - \"How it works\" quick explainer\n- [ ] **Geo-tag all photos** before uploading (add GPS coordinates for Miami area)\n- [ ] **Name photo files** with keywords before uploading (e.g., \"20-yard-dumpster-rental-miami-fl.jpg\" not \"IMG_4582.jpg\")\n\n#### E. Google Posts (GBP Updates)\n- [ ] **Post 2x per week minimum.** Types to rotate:\n  - Offer posts (\"$299 for 10-yard dumpster — same-day delivery!\")\n  - What's New posts (\"Now serving Broward County!\")\n  - Event posts (seasonal: spring cleaning, hurricane prep)\n  - Before/after project highlights\n  - Customer testimonial highlights\n  - Tips (\"What size dumpster do I need?\")\n- [ ] Include a CTA button on every post (\"Call Now\", \"Book Online\", \"Get Quote\")\n- [ ] Include 1-2 relevant keywords naturally in each post\n- [ ] Add a photo or video to EVERY post\n\n#### F. Reviews Strategy\n- [ ] **Current status:** Appears to have solid 5-star reviews with owner responses ✅\n- [ ] **Target:** 5+ new Google reviews per week\n- [ ] **Review request process (set up):**\n  - [ ] Create a direct Google review link (from GBP Manager → Share Review Form)\n  - [ ] Text/email the link to every customer after service completion\n  - [ ] Train drivers to ask for reviews verbally at pickup\n  - [ ] Add review link to invoice/receipt emails\n  - [ ] Add review link to website thank-you page\n  - [ ] Create a QR code with the review link for business cards/magnets\n- [ ] **Review response policy:**\n  - [ ] Respond to ALL reviews within 24 hours (you're already doing this ✅)\n  - [ ] Include keywords naturally in responses (you're doing this well ✅)\n  - [ ] For negative reviews: acknowledge, apologize, offer to resolve offline\n- [ ] **Keyword seeding in reviews:** Encourage customers to mention specifics: dumpster size, city, project type (e.g., \"Great 20-yard dumpster for our Doral renovation\")\n\n#### G. Q&A Section\n- [ ] **Seed 10-15 FAQ questions yourself** (you can ask and answer your own questions):\n  - \"What size dumpster do I need for a kitchen renovation?\"\n  - \"Do you offer same-day dumpster delivery in Miami?\"\n  - \"How much does a 20-yard dumpster cost?\"\n  - \"Can I put concrete in a dumpster?\"\n  - \"Do I need a permit for a dumpster in my driveway?\"\n  - \"What areas do you serve?\"\n  - \"How long can I keep the dumpster?\"\n  - \"Do you offer dumpsters for construction sites?\"\n  - \"What can't go in a dumpster?\"\n  - \"Do you deliver dumpsters on weekends?\"\n  - \"Is there a weight limit on dumpsters?\"\n  - \"How quickly can you deliver a dumpster?\"\n  - \"Do you offer recycling services?\"\n- [ ] Answer each with keyword-rich, helpful responses\n- [ ] Monitor for new customer questions weekly and answer promptly\n\n---\n\n## PART 2: WEBSITE SEO AUDIT\n\n### 🔍 Current Website: usadumpsterrentals.net\n\n#### A. Critical Issues Found\n- [ ] **⚠️ DUAL DOMAIN PROBLEM:** The site links to usascrapmetalcompany.com for dumpster rental too. This CONFUSES Google. Pick ONE primary domain for dumpster services and redirect or canonicalize the other\n  - **Recommendation:** usadumpsterrentals.net = dumpster services. usascrapmetalcompany.com = scrap metal only. Remove dumpster content from scrap metal site OR use canonical tags pointing to usadumpsterrentals.net\n- [ ] **⚠️ BUSINESS NAME INCONSISTENCY:** \"USA Dumpster Rentals\" on website vs \"USA Dumpster and Recycling\" on directories. PICK ONE and make it consistent everywhere\n- [ ] **⚠️ GBP response mentions \"USA Scrap Metal & Recycling Team\"** on what appears to be a dumpster review. Keep brand responses consistent — always sign as the dumpster brand on dumpster reviews\n\n#### B. Title Tags & Meta Descriptions\n- [ ] **Homepage title tag** — Current: \"Same Day Dumpster Rental Service in Miami FL\"\n  - **Suggested:** \"USA Dumpster Rentals | Same-Day Roll-Off Dumpster Rental in Miami FL\"\n- [ ] Create unique title tags for every page. Format: \"[Service] | [City] | USA Dumpster Rentals\"\n  - Examples:\n  - \"10 Yard Dumpster Rental Miami | Starting at $XXX | USA Dumpster Rentals\"\n  - \"Construction Dumpster Rental Miami | 20, 30, 40 Yard | USA Dumpster Rentals\"\n  - \"Residential Dumpster Rental Miami | Home Cleanout Dumpsters | USA Dumpster\"\n- [ ] Write unique meta descriptions (150-160 chars) for every page with CTA (\"Call now for same-day delivery!\")\n\n#### C. Service Pages (Create or Optimize)\n- [ ] **Individual page for each dumpster size:**\n  - [ ] /10-yard-dumpster-rental-miami/\n  - [ ] /20-yard-dumpster-rental-miami/\n  - [ ] /30-yard-dumpster-rental-miami/\n  - [ ] /40-yard-dumpster-rental-miami/\n- [ ] **Individual page for each service type:**\n  - [ ] /construction-dumpster-rental-miami/ (exists — audit and optimize)\n  - [ ] /residential-dumpster-rental/ (exists — add city to URL if possible)\n  - [ ] /commercial-dumpster-rental-miami/ (create)\n  - [ ] /junk-removal-miami/ (create)\n  - [ ] /demolition-dumpster-rental-miami/ (create)\n  - [ ] /same-day-dumpster-rental-miami/ (create — high-intent keyword)\n- [ ] Each page needs: H1 with keyword, 800+ words of unique content, photos, pricing info, FAQ section, CTA, schema markup\n\n#### D. City/Area Pages\n- [ ] **Create a dedicated page for each major service city:**\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-doral/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-hialeah/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-coral-gables/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-miami-beach/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-north-miami/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-fort-lauderdale/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-hollywood-fl/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-pembroke-pines/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-miramar/\n  - [ ] /dumpster-rental-aventura/\n  - [ ] (continue for all service area cities)\n- [ ] Each city page needs: unique content about that city, service details, local landmarks/references, embedded Google Map, reviews from customers in that city, local phone number\n\n#### E. Schema Markup (Structured Data)\n- [ ] **LocalBusiness schema** on every page (business name, address, phone, hours, service area)\n- [ ] **Service schema** for each dumpster size/service\n- [ ] **FAQ schema** on FAQ sections (enables rich results in Google)\n- [ ] **Review/AggregateRating schema** (pulls star ratings into search results)\n- [ ] **Product schema** for each dumpster size with pricing\n- [ ] Test all schema at: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results\n\n#### F. Technical SEO\n- [ ] **Page speed:** Test at PageSpeed Insights (https://pagespeed.web.dev/) — target 90+ mobile score\n- [ ] **Mobile-friendly:** Test at Google's mobile-friendly test\n- [ ] **XML sitemap:** Verify sitemap exists at /sitemap.xml and is submitted in Google Search Console\n- [ ] **Robots.txt:** Check /robots.txt — ensure nothing important is blocked\n- [ ] **SSL:** Verify HTTPS is active (appears to be ✅)\n- [ ] **Core Web Vitals:** Check in Google Search Console → Experience → Core Web Vitals\n- [ ] **Internal linking:** Every service page should link to related pages (e.g., 10-yard page links to 20-yard, city pages link to service pages)\n- [ ] **Image optimization:** Compress all images, add alt text with keywords (e.g., alt=\"20 yard dumpster rental in Doral FL\")\n\n#### G. Content Marketing\n- [ ] **Start a blog** at /blog/ with SEO-optimized articles:\n  - \"How to Choose the Right Dumpster Size for Your Project\"\n  - \"Dumpster Rental Prices in Miami: 2026 Complete Guide\"\n  - \"What Can You Put in a Roll-Off Dumpster?\"\n  - \"Do You Need a Permit for a Dumpster in Miami?\"\n  - \"10 vs 20 Yard Dumpster: Which One Do You Need?\"\n  - \"Best Dump Sites in Miami-Dade County\"\n  - \"Spring Cleaning Dumpster Rental Guide\"\n  - \"Hurricane Cleanup: Dumpster Rental for Storm Debris\"\n  - \"Contractor's Guide to Dumpster Rental in South Florida\"\n- [ ] Target 1 new blog post per week\n- [ ] Each post: 1,500+ words, keyword-optimized, internal links, images, CTA\n\n#### H. Citation Audit (NAP Consistency)\n- [ ] **Check and fix business info on ALL of these directories** (name, address, phone must be IDENTICAL):\n  - [ ] Google Business Profile\n  - [ ] Yelp\n  - [ ] Facebook Business Page\n  - [ ] Bing Places\n  - [ ] Apple Maps\n  - [ ] BBB (Better Business Bureau)\n  - [ ] Angi (HomeAdvisor)\n  - [ ] Thumbtack\n  - [ ] Nextdoor Business\n  - [ ] Yellow Pages (YP.com)\n  - [ ] Manta\n  - [ ] Foursquare\n  - [ ] Citysearch\n  - [ ] MapQuest\n  - [ ] DexKnows\n  - [ ] ScrapMonster (you're already listed here)\n  - [ ] Superpages\n  - [ ] Local.com\n  - [ ] Chamber of Commerce (Miami)\n  - [ ] Alignable\n- [ ] **Use the EXACT same format everywhere:**\n  - Business Name: [pick one and use it everywhere]\n  - Address: 3147 NW North River Dr, Suite #2, Miami, FL 33142\n  - Phone: [same number everywhere]\n  - Website: usadumpsterrentals.net\n\n---\n\n## PART 3: PERFORMANCE MAX (PMax) CAMPAIGN CHECKLIST\n\n### 📣 Setup & Configuration\n\n#### A. Pre-Launch Requirements\n- [ ] **Link GBP to Google Ads account** (Settings → Linked accounts → Google Business Profile)\n- [ ] **Set up conversion tracking** BEFORE launching PMax:\n  - [ ] Phone calls from ads (Google forwarding number)\n  - [ ] Phone calls from website (import via GTM or call tracking)\n  - [ ] Contact form submissions\n  - [ ] Book Now / quote request form submissions\n  - [ ] Click-to-call on mobile\n- [ ] **Install Google Tag Manager (GTM)** on usadumpsterrentals.net if not already\n- [ ] **Set up Google Analytics 4 (GA4)** and link to Google Ads\n- [ ] **Configure Enhanced Conversions** (passes hashed customer data for better attribution)\n- [ ] **Import offline conversions** if possible (phone leads that become customers)\n\n#### B. PMax Campaign Structure\n- [ ] **Campaign 1: Core Dumpster Rental (highest budget)**\n  - Asset Group 1: \"Dumpster Rental Miami\" (high-intent, local)\n  - Asset Group 2: \"Roll-Off Dumpster Rental\" (product-specific)\n  - Asset Group 3: \"Construction Dumpster\" (contractor audience)\n  - Asset Group 4: \"Same-Day Dumpster Delivery\" (urgency buyers)\n\n- [ ] **Campaign 2: Service-Specific (moderate budget)**\n  - Asset Group 1: \"Residential Cleanout Dumpsters\"\n  - Asset Group 2: \"Junk Removal & Debris Hauling\"\n  - Asset Group 3: \"Commercial Waste Services\"\n\n- [ ] **Campaign 3: Branded (low budget, high ROAS)**\n  - Asset Group 1: \"USA Dumpster Rentals\" branded terms\n  - (Protect your brand name from competitors bidding on it)\n\n#### C. Asset Requirements (Per Asset Group)\n- [ ] **Headlines (minimum 5, recommend 15):**\n  - Short headlines (30 chars): \"Dumpster Rental Miami\", \"Same-Day Delivery\", \"10-40 Yard Dumpsters\", \"Free Quotes\", \"Licensed & Insured\"\n  - Long headlines (90 chars): \"Fast & Affordable Roll-Off Dumpster Rental in Miami FL — Same-Day Delivery Available\"\n- [ ] **Descriptions (minimum 2, recommend 5):**\n  - \"Need a dumpster today? USA Dumpster Rentals offers same-day roll-off dumpster delivery in Miami. 10, 20, 30, 40 yard sizes. Call now for a free quote!\"\n  - \"Professional dumpster rental for construction, residential cleanouts, and commercial projects in Miami-Dade & Broward. Licensed, insured, affordable.\"\n- [ ] **Images (minimum 3, recommend 15+):**\n  - [ ] Landscape images (1200x628): fleet shots, dumpsters on-site, before/after\n  - [ ] Square images (1200x1200): dumpster close-ups, team photos, logos\n  - [ ] Portrait images (960x1200): for Stories/Reels placements\n  - [ ] All images should be high-quality, branded, show real trucks/dumpsters\n- [ ] **Videos (highly recommended):**\n  - [ ] 30-second dumpster delivery video\n  - [ ] 15-second before/after cleanup\n  - [ ] 60-second company overview\n  - [ ] Vertical (9:16) for YouTube Shorts placements\n- [ ] **Business name and logo** assets\n- [ ] **Call-to-action:** \"Call Now\", \"Get Quote\", \"Book Online\"\n\n#### D. Audience Signals (Tell Google Who to Target)\n- [ ] **Custom Segments (Search Themes):**\n  - \"dumpster rental near me\"\n  - \"roll off dumpster Miami\"\n  - \"construction dumpster rental\"\n  - \"junk removal Miami\"\n  - \"10 yard dumpster\"\n  - \"20 yard dumpster rental\"\n  - \"dumpster rental same day\"\n  - \"trash dumpster rental\"\n  - \"debris removal Miami\"\n- [ ] **In-Market Audiences:**\n  - Home Improvement\n  - Construction & Renovation\n  - Waste Management Services\n  - Moving & Relocation\n- [ ] **Custom Audiences (URL-based):**\n  - Competitors' websites (waste management companies in Miami)\n  - Home improvement sites\n  - Construction supply sites\n- [ ] **Customer Lists (if available):**\n  - Upload past customer email/phone lists for lookalike targeting\n  - Create exclusion lists (current active customers if you don't want to advertise to them)\n\n#### E. Geo-Targeting\n- [ ] Set location targeting to your actual service area:\n  - Target: Miami-Dade County + Broward County\n  - OR target specific cities/ZIPs for more control\n  - Use \"Presence\" targeting (people IN these locations), NOT \"Presence or Interest\"\n- [ ] Set location bid adjustments if certain areas are more profitable\n- [ ] Exclude areas you DON'T serve\n\n#### F. Budget & Bidding\n- [ ] **Starting budget recommendation:** $100-$200/day for PMax (adjust based on your market)\n- [ ] **Bidding strategy:**\n  - Start with \"Maximize Conversions\" for first 2-3 weeks (let Google learn)\n  - Once you have 30+ conversions, switch to \"Target CPA\" with your target cost-per-lead\n  - Eventually test \"Target ROAS\" if you can track revenue per lead\n- [ ] **Day parting:** Consider higher bids during business hours (7AM-7PM) when you can answer calls immediately\n- [ ] **Seasonal adjustments:** Increase budget 20-30% during spring (March-May) and hurricane season\n\n#### G. Ongoing Optimization Checklist (Weekly)\n- [ ] Check asset performance: replace \"Low\" performing headlines, descriptions, and images\n- [ ] Review Search Themes: add new relevant themes, pause irrelevant ones\n- [ ] Check placement reports: exclude irrelevant Display/YouTube placements\n- [ ] Monitor conversion data: are leads converting to actual customers?\n- [ ] Review geographic performance: which cities/ZIPs produce the best leads?\n- [ ] A/B test new ad creatives monthly\n- [ ] Review auction insights: who are you competing against?\n\n---\n\n## PART 4: ADDITIONAL GOOGLE ADS RECOMMENDATIONS\n\n### 🔍 Standard Search Campaigns (Run Alongside PMax)\n- [ ] **Create a dedicated Search campaign** for highest-intent keywords:\n  - [Exact match] \"dumpster rental miami\"\n  - [Exact match] \"roll off dumpster miami\"\n  - [Exact match] \"dumpster rental near me\"\n  - [Phrase match] \"dumpster rental miami fl\"\n  - [Phrase match] \"10 yard dumpster miami\"\n  - [Phrase match] \"construction dumpster miami\"\n  - [Phrase match] \"same day dumpster rental\"\n- [ ] Search campaigns give you MORE CONTROL over keywords than PMax\n- [ ] Run both: PMax for broad coverage + Search for high-intent precision\n\n### 📍 Google Local Services Ads (LSA)\n- [ ] **SET UP LSA — THIS IS THE #1 PRIORITY**\n  - LSA ads appear ABOVE regular Google Ads\n  - You only pay per LEAD, not per click\n  - Shows your Google Guaranteed badge\n- [ ] Where to set up: ads.google.com/local-services-ads\n- [ ] Requirements:\n  - [ ] Pass Google's background check\n  - [ ] Proof of insurance\n  - [ ] Proof of license\n  - [ ] Set service areas and job types\n  - [ ] Get enough Google reviews (minimum 5, more = better ranking)\n- [ ] Budget: Start at $50-$100/week and increase as leads come in\n- [ ] Dispute bad leads within 30 days for credit\n\n---\n\n## PART 5: PRIORITY ACTION ITEMS (START HERE)\n\n### 🔴 IMMEDIATE (This Week)\n1. Fix business name consistency across GBP, website, and all directories\n2. Resolve dual-domain issue (usadumpsterrentals.net vs usascrapmetalcompany.com)\n3. Apply for Google Local Services Ads (LSA)\n4. Link GBP to Google Ads account\n5. Set up conversion tracking (GTM + phone call tracking)\n\n### 🟡 SHORT-TERM (Next 2 Weeks)\n6. Optimize GBP description, categories, services, and Q&A\n7. Upload 50+ new photos to GBP (geo-tagged, keyword-named)\n8. Start GBP posting schedule (2x/week)\n9. Implement review request automation\n10. Create/optimize service pages on website (each dumpster size + service type)\n\n### 🟢 MEDIUM-TERM (Next 30 Days)\n11. Build city-specific landing pages (start with top 10 cities)\n12. Add schema markup to all pages\n13. Launch PMax campaign with proper asset groups\n14. Launch standard Search campaign for high-intent keywords\n15. Begin citation audit and cleanup across 20+ directories\n\n### 🔵 ONGOING (Monthly)\n16. Publish 4 blog posts per month\n17. Upload 10+ new GBP photos per month\n18. Post on GBP 8+ times per month\n19. Generate 20+ new Google reviews per month\n20. Optimize PMax assets weekly (replace low performers)\n21. A/B test ad creatives monthly\n22. Monitor and respond to all reviews within 24 hours\n\n---\n\n*Document saved to: audits/usa-dumpster-gbp-seo-pmax-audit.md*\n*Prepared by Master Agent for USA Dumpster & Recycling*\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":6703,"cacheRead":11062,"cacheWrite":135743,"totalTokens":153509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773781564768}}
