dumpster tracking, driver management, automated billing, online ordering, SEO, and Quickbooks compatible. All with one tool that’s easy for Waste Haulers to use.\n\nWant to see Docket in action? Fill out the form to get started!\n\n## Keep What Works.\nSimplify The Rest.\n\nCustomer and job management, dumpster tracking, driver management, automated billing, online ordering, SEO, and Quickbooks compatible. All with one tool that’s easy for Waste Haulers to use.\n\nA customer finds your website and rents a dumpster. You collect payment via your online shopping cart and the customer picks an available dumpster, drop off location, date and time. You can also:\n\n- Set up automatic pricing based on zip code\n\n- Add terms and conditions\n\n- Have the customer select material types\n\n- And more\n\nA customer finds your website and rents a dumpster. You collect payment via your online shopping cart and the customer picks an available dumpster, drop off location, date and time. You can also:\n\n- Set up automatic pricing based on zip code\n\n- Add terms and conditions\n\n- Have the customer select material types\n\n- And more\n\nGET STARTED TODAY!\n\nInstead of manually picking a driver or guessing on routes, IronRouteAI automatically analyzes your day and recommends the best driver and route based on dump fees, materials, bin sizes, distance, fuel costs, and workload.\n\nIronRoute AI helps you:\n\n- Route trucks to the right dump to lower dump fees\n\n- Reduce fuel costs by cutting unnecessary miles\n\n- Shorten drive time with smarter stop order and routing\n\n- And much more\n\nInstead of manually picking a driver or guessing on routes, IronRouteAI automatically analyzes your day and recommends the best driver and route based on dump fees, materials, bin sizes, distance, fuel costs, and workload.\n\nIronRoute AI helps you:\n\n- Route trucks to the right dump to lower dump fees\n\n- Reduce fuel costs by cutting unnecessary miles\n\n- Shorten drive time with smarter stop order and routing\n\n- And much more\n\nOnce your driver is on their way, a text message gets sent to your customer with an ETA. Your customer can even track your driver live on a map. And:\n\n- Your driver gets turn by turn directions to the drop off location.\n\n- The driver drops off the dumpster, snaps a photo of the dumpster, driveway, etc.\n\nOnce your driver is on their way, a text message gets sent to your customer with an ETA. Your customer can even track your driver live on a map. And:\n\n- Your driver gets turn by turn directions to the drop off location.\n\n- The driver drops off the dumpster, snaps a photo of the dumpster, driveway, etc.\n\nUsing the Docket mobile app, your driver scans the dumpster. Uh oh. Your driver notices 4 bald tires in the dumpster and the dumpster is overweight. No problem! In the mobile app your driver can:\n\n- Add extra charges, and take pictures to show the customer.\n\n- Record the weight, tonnage, materials, and where it’s dumped.\n\n- Check the dumpster back into the yard.\n\n- And more.\n\nUsing the Docket mobile app, your driver scans the dumpster. Uh oh. Your driver notices 4 bald tires in the dumpster and the dumpster is overweight. No problem! In the mobile app your driver can:\n\n- Add extra charges, and take pictures to show the customer.\n\n- Record the weight, tonnage, materials, and where it’s dumped.\n\n- Check the dumpster back into the yard.\n\n- And more.\n\nIt’s time to charge the customer’s credit card for the additional charges. \n\n- With the click of a button you charge the customer for any additional fees like, mattresses, tires, concrete, weight overages, etc.\n\n- If the rental went longer than originally agreed upon, we’d charge for that too\n\nIt’s time to charge the customer’s credit card for the additional charges.\n\n- With the click of a button you charge the customer for any additional fees like, mattresses, tires, concrete, weight overages, etc.\n\n- If the rental went longer than originally agreed upon, we’d charge for that too.\n\nThink about Docket’s reports as your crystal ball. They help you make solid business decisions with confidence. Some popular reports are:\n\n- Driver Performance\n\n- Sales Performance\n\n- Asset Performance\n\n- Dumpster Aging\n\n- And many more\n\nThink about Docket’s reports as your crystal ball. They help you make solid business decisions with confidence. Some popular reports are:\n\n- Driver Performance\n\n- Sales Performance\n\n- Asset Performance\n\n- Dumpster Aging\n\n- And many more\n\n## Built Just For\nDumpster Rental Software\n\nCustomer and job management, dumpster tracking, driver management, automated billing, online ordering, SEO, and Quickbooks compatible. All with one tool that’s easy for Waste Haulers to use.\n\nWant to see Docket in action? Fill out the form to get started!\n\n- [Dumpster Rental Software](https://www.yourdocket.com/dumpster-rental-software/)\n- [Junk Removal Software](https://www.yourdocket.com/junk-removal-software/)\n\n- [Customer Support](https://support.yourdocket.com/hc/en-us)\n- [Submit A Request](https://support.yourdocket.com/hc/en-us/requests/new)\n- [System Status](https://status.yourdocket.com/)\n\n- [Careers](https://www.yourdocket.com/careers/)\n- [FAQs](https://www.yourdocket.com/faq/)\n- [Partnerships](https://www.yourdocket.com/partners/)\n- [Terms of Service](https://www.yourdocket.com/terms-of-service/)\n- [Privacy Policy](https://www.yourdocket.com/privacy-policy/)\n\n- [Blog](https://www.yourdocket.com/blog/)\n- [Rolloff Rundowns](https://www.yourdocket.com/rolloff-rundowns/)\n- [Case Studies](https://www.yourdocket.com/case-study/)\n\n- [Asset Tracking](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/asset-tracking/)\n- [Billing & Payments](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/billing-payments/)\n- [Brokers Tools](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/brokers-tools/)\n- [Customer Portal](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/customer-portal/)\n- [Driver Management](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/driver-management/)\n- [Online Ordering](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/online-ordering/)\n- [Reports](https://www.yourdocket.com/features/reports/)\n- [Scheduling & Dispatching](https://www.yourdocket.com/scheduling-dispatching/)\n\n [Go to Top](#)\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"27bc4894d5cf3011\">>>"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773800691377}}
