{"type":"message","id":"a93104a9","parentId":"16c48f74","timestamp":"2026-03-18T02:25:01.395Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01YK4R8Mr3EVgh9Pr5VHrTdx","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Tuesday, March 17th, 2026 — 10:25 PM (America/New_York)\n🧠 Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6 · 🔑 token (anthropic:default)\n🧮 Tokens: 10 in / 8.1k out\n🗄️ Cache: 7% hit · 11k cached, 138k new\n📚 Context: 149k/200k (75%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:whatsapp:group:120363425630314527@g.us • updated 1m ago\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n👥 Activation: mention · 🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:whatsapp:group:120363425630314527@g.us","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Tuesday, March 17th, 2026 — 10:25 PM (America/New_York)\n🧠 Model: anthropic/claude-opus-4-6 · 🔑 token (anthropic:default)\n🧮 Tokens: 10 in / 8.1k out\n🗄️ Cache: 7% hit · 11k cached, 138k new\n📚 Context: 149k/200k (75%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n🧵 Session: agent:main:whatsapp:group:120363425630314527@g.us • updated 1m ago\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n👥 Activation: mention · 🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773800701392}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f2c2b48","parentId":"a93104a9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T02:27:17.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good — 75% context used. I have enough for the master plan but need to be efficient. Let me save the full plan to a document rather than burning all remaining context in chat."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01GfViVwXL5hn1X3CBjgfFop","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace/projects/saas-platform/MASTER-PLAN.md","content":"# 🚀 MASTER PLAN: Roll-Off Waste Industry SaaS Platform\n## \"Docket Killer\" — Build, Operate, Broker, Dominate\n### Date: March 17, 2026\n### Prepared by: Master Agent (👑) — Coordinating ALL 32 Agents\n\n---\n\n## EXECUTIVE SUMMARY\n\n**Vision:** Build a proprietary SaaS platform for the roll-off waste/dumpster industry that is a better, more comprehensive version of Docket (yourdocket.com) — with integrated SEO, paid ads management, call tracking + transcription, training academy, AI agents, and a *broker marketplace* that lets you operate asset-light in any market nationwide.\n\n**End State:** Own the largest database of haulers AND customers in Florida → then nationally. Monetize through SaaS subscriptions, brokered loads, ad management fees, and marketplace transaction fees.\n\n**Why This Wins:** Docket gives haulers software. YOU give haulers software + marketing + leads + AI + broker network — a complete business-in-a-box that makes them dependent on your ecosystem.\n\n---\n\n## PART 1: COMPETITIVE ANALYSIS — DOCKET TEARDOWN\n\n### What Docket Offers (3 Tiers: Grow, Pro, Pro Plus)\n\n| Feature | Docket Has It | Our Platform Must Beat It |\n|---------|--------------|--------------------------|\n| Customer Management | ✅ | ✅ + AI-powered CRM |\n| Scheduling & Dispatching | ✅ | ✅ + AI route optimization (smarter than IronRouteAI) |\n| Driver Mobile App | ✅ | ✅ + offline mode, voice commands, AI assistant |\n| Asset/Dumpster Tracking | ✅ GPS + QR | ✅ + IoT fill-level sensors, predictive swap |\n| Billing & Payments | ✅ 2.8-3% + 30¢ | ✅ Lower processing fees (2.5% + 25¢) |\n| Online Ordering/Shopping Cart | ✅ Basic/Premium | ✅ + AI chatbot ordering, dynamic pricing |\n| Broker Tools | ✅ Basic | ✅ + Full marketplace with hauler network |\n| QuickBooks Integration | ✅ | ✅ + Xero, FreshBooks, Sage |\n| Samsara Integration | ✅ | ✅ + Geotab, Verizon Connect, any GPS |\n| Custom Website | ✅ | ✅ + SEO-optimized, A/B tested, conversion-focused |\n| Local SEO | ✅ Basic | ✅ + Full SEO suite with rank tracking |\n| Text/SMS Messaging | ✅ 500-1000/mo | ✅ Unlimited (Twilio-based) |\n| IronRouteAI (route optimization) | ✅ Pro Plus only | ✅ All tiers + superior ML engine |\n| Review Guard | ✅ | ✅ + AI review response drafting |\n| Mailchimp Integration | ✅ | ✅ + native email marketing |\n| Dumpsters.com Integration | ✅ | ✅ + our own marketplace |\n\n### What Docket DOESN'T Have (Our Competitive Moat)\n\n| Feature | Docket | Our Platform |\n|---------|--------|-------------|\n| Google Ads Management | ❌ | ✅ Built-in PPC management + AI optimization |\n| Meta/Facebook Ads | ❌ | ✅ Built-in social ads management |\n| Call Tracking & Recording | ❌ | ✅ Every call tracked, recorded, transcribed |\n| AI Call Transcription & Analysis | ❌ | ✅ Real-time transcription + sentiment + coaching |\n| AI Sales Agent (phone/chat) | ❌ | ✅ AI answers calls, qualifies leads, books jobs |\n| Training Academy (LMS) | ❌ | ✅ Video training for drivers, dispatch, sales |\n| Broker Marketplace | ❌ (basic tools) | ✅ Full 2-sided marketplace (Uber for dumpsters) |\n| AI Demand Forecasting | ❌ | ✅ Predict demand by area/season |\n| Dynamic Pricing Engine | ❌ | ✅ AI adjusts prices based on supply/demand |\n| Competitor Price Monitoring | ❌ | ✅ Scrape and track competitor pricing |\n| Multi-location Dashboard | ❌ | ✅ Franchise/multi-branch management |\n| White-label Option | ❌ | ✅ Haulers can rebrand as their own |\n| National Hauler Database | ❌ | ✅ Our core data asset |\n| Customer Database Ownership | ❌ | ✅ We own the demand data |\n\n---\n\n## PART 2: PLATFORM ARCHITECTURE\n\n### Core Modules (15 Modules)\n\n**MODULE 1: Operations Hub (Docket Equivalent + Better)**\n- Order management (delivery, swap, pickup, dump & return, live load)\n- Scheduling & dispatch dashboard\n- AI route optimization (replaces IronRouteAI)\n- Driver mobile app (iOS + Android, offline-first)\n- Asset tracking (GPS, QR, RFID, IoT fill sensors)\n- Customer portal (order, track, pay, review)\n- Online ordering with dynamic pricing by ZIP\n- Billing, invoicing, payments (Stripe, ACH)\n- QuickBooks/Xero sync\n- Samsara/Geotab/Verizon Connect integration\n- Text/email notifications (30+ automated triggers)\n- Photo proof of delivery/pickup\n- Weight/tonnage tracking and overage billing\n\n**MODULE 2: Marketing Suite (UNIQUE — Docket has nothing like this)**\n- Built-in SEO toolkit\n  - Keyword rank tracking\n  - On-page SEO audit tool\n  - Local citation management\n  - GBP optimization assistant\n  - Schema markup generator\n  - Content suggestions powered by AI\n- Google Ads management\n  - Campaign creation wizard\n  - Automated bid optimization\n  - Keyword suggestions by market\n  - Performance dashboards\n  - Budget pacing and alerts\n  - Google Ads API integration\n- Meta Ads management\n  - Campaign creation and management\n  - Audience builder (lookalikes, custom)\n  - Creative asset library\n  - Performance reporting\n  - Meta Marketing API integration\n- Bing Ads integration\n- YouTube Ads management\n- Review management\n  - Automated review request sequences\n  - AI-drafted review responses\n  - Multi-platform monitoring (Google, Yelp, BBB)\n  - Review analytics and sentiment\n\n**MODULE 3: Call Intelligence**\n- Call tracking numbers (local + toll-free)\n- Call recording and storage\n- AI call transcription (real-time)\n- Call sentiment analysis\n- Lead scoring from call content\n- Missed call alerts and callback automation\n- Call coaching insights (identify what closes deals)\n- Call-to-conversion attribution (which ad/keyword drove the call)\n- Integration: Twilio Voice API + OpenAI Whisper + custom NLP\n\n**MODULE 4: AI Agent Suite**\n- AI Phone Agent (answers calls 24/7, qualifies leads, books jobs)\n- AI Chat Agent (website chatbot, WhatsApp, SMS)\n- AI Email Agent (responds to inquiries, sends quotes)\n- AI Dispatch Assistant (suggests optimal assignments)\n- AI Pricing Agent (recommends pricing by market conditions)\n- AI Review Responder (drafts personalized review responses)\n- AI Sales Coach (analyzes calls, provides tips)\n- Integration: OpenAI API, Anthropic Claude API, ElevenLabs (voice)\n\n**MODULE 5: Training Academy (LMS)**\n- Video course platform for hauler employees\n- Course categories:\n  - Driver safety training\n  - CDL compliance\n  - Customer service excellence\n  - Dispatch operations\n  - Sales and closing\n  - Equipment maintenance\n  - Software training (how to use the platform)\n- Quizzes and certifications\n- Progress tracking and compliance reporting\n- Content creation tools for custom courses\n- Integration: Mux (video hosting), custom LMS engine\n\n**MODULE 6: Broker Marketplace (\"Uber for Dumpsters\")**\n- Two-sided marketplace:\n  - DEMAND SIDE: Customers/brokers post dumpster needs\n  - SUPPLY SIDE: Haulers with available inventory accept jobs\n- Real-time availability and pricing by market\n- Hauler network management (onboarding, verification, rating)\n- Automated job matching (customer need → nearest available hauler)\n- Broker tools:\n  - White-label customer-facing experience\n  - Markup/margin management\n  - Hauler payout automation\n  - Customer communication management\n  - Job progress monitoring\n- Nationwide coverage through hauler network (no assets needed)\n- Commission/transaction fee model (10-20% per brokered load)\n- Integration: Stripe Connect for marketplace payments\n\n**MODULE 7: Customer Database & CRM**\n- Unified customer database (the CORE asset)\n- Customer profiles with full history\n- Lead scoring and pipeline management\n- Automated follow-up sequences\n- Customer segmentation (residential, commercial, contractor)\n- Win-back campaigns for churned customers\n- Referral tracking\n- Integration with all marketing and operations modules\n\n**MODULE 8: Analytics & Business Intelligence**\n- Revenue dashboards (by truck, route, customer, market)\n- Marketing ROI dashboards (by channel, campaign, keyword)\n- Operational efficiency metrics\n- Financial reporting (P&L by service line)\n- Competitor benchmarking\n- Market sizing by ZIP/city\n- Predictive analytics (demand forecasting, churn prediction)\n- Custom report builder\n- Integration: Metabase or custom dashboards\n\n**MODULE 9: Website Builder**\n- Template-based website builder for haulers\n- SEO-optimized templates\n- Integrated online ordering\n- Blog engine\n- Landing page builder (for PPC campaigns)\n- Mobile-responsive\n- Custom domain support\n- A/B testing capabilities\n\n**MODULE 10: Communication Hub**\n- Unified inbox (calls, texts, emails, chat in one place)\n- Automated text/email sequences (30+ triggers)\n- Two-way SMS\n- Email marketing (newsletters, promotions)\n- WhatsApp Business integration\n- Push notifications (mobile app)\n- VoIP phone system integration\n\n**MODULE 11: Payments & Billing**\n- Online payment processing (Stripe)\n- ACH payments\n- Recurring billing for commercial accounts\n- Automated invoicing\n- Late payment reminders and automation\n- Payment plans\n- Surcharge management (fuel, environmental fees)\n- Overage and additional charge workflows\n- Integration: Stripe, Plaid (for ACH)\n\n**MODULE 12: Fleet & Asset Management**\n- Dumpster inventory (size, location, condition, age)\n- Truck fleet tracking\n- Maintenance scheduling and alerts\n- Integration with Samsara, Geotab, Verizon Connect\n- Driver management and performance\n- Fuel tracking\n- DOT compliance tracking\n\n**MODULE 13: Compliance & Documents**\n- Digital service agreements and contracts\n- E-signature integration (DocuSign/HelloSign API)\n- Permit management\n- Insurance certificate management\n- Weight ticket management\n- Document storage per customer/job\n\n**MODULE 14: Multi-Tenant & White-Label**\n- Multi-tenant architecture (each hauler is a tenant)\n- White-label option (haulers rebrand as their own)\n- Multi-location support (franchises, multi-branch)\n- Role-based access control (owner, dispatcher, driver, accountant)\n- Custom branding per tenant\n\n**MODULE 15: Admin & Platform Management**\n- Super-admin dashboard (YOUR view of all tenants)\n- Platform analytics (MRR, churn, usage, growth)\n- Tenant onboarding automation\n- Feature flag management\n- Billing and subscription management (Stripe Billing)\n- Support ticket system\n\n---\n\n## PART 3: TECHNOLOGY STACK & APIs\n\n### Backend\n- **Framework:** Node.js (NestJS) or Python (FastAPI)\n- **Database:** PostgreSQL + PostGIS (geospatial)\n- **Cache:** Redis\n- **Queue:** BullMQ or RabbitMQ\n- **Search:** Meilisearch or Elasticsearch\n- **File Storage:** AWS S3\n\n### Frontend\n- **Web App:** Next.js 14+ (React) with TypeScript\n- **UI:** Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui\n- **Maps:** Mapbox GL JS\n- **Charts:** Recharts + D3.js\n\n### Mobile\n- **Driver App:** React Native (iOS + Android)\n- **Offline:** WatermelonDB\n- **Push Notifications:** Firebase Cloud Messaging\n\n### Infrastructure\n- **Cloud:** AWS (primary)\n- **Containers:** Docker + ECS (or Kubernetes later)\n- **CI/CD:** GitHub Actions\n- **CDN:** CloudFront\n- **Monitoring:** Datadog\n- **Error Tracking:** Sentry\n\n### Key API Integrations\n| API | Purpose | Est. Cost |\n|-----|---------|-----------|\n| **Stripe + Stripe Connect** | Payments + marketplace payouts | 2.9% + 30¢ per txn |\n| **Twilio Voice + SMS** | Call tracking, recording, SMS | ~$0.015/min voice, $0.0079/SMS |\n| **OpenAI Whisper** | Call transcription | ~$0.006/min |\n| **OpenAI GPT-4 / Claude** | AI agents, chat, analysis | ~$0.01-0.03/1K tokens |\n| **ElevenLabs** | AI voice agent | ~$0.30/min |\n| **Google Ads API** | Campaign management | Free (API) |\n| **Meta Marketing API** | Facebook/Instagram ads | Free (API) |\n| **Microsoft Ads API** | Bing ads management | Free (API) |\n| **Google Maps Platform** | Geocoding, routing, maps | ~$7/1K requests |\n| **Mapbox** | Maps in dashboard/app | Free tier then $0.50/1K |\n| **Samsara API** | Fleet telematics | Included with Samsara subscription |\n| **Geotab API** | Fleet telematics | Included with Geotab subscription |\n| **QuickBooks Online API** | Accounting sync | Free (Intuit developer) |\n| **Xero API** | Accounting sync | Free (Xero partner) |\n| **Plaid** | ACH bank payments | $0.30-$1.50/verification |\n| **DocuSign/HelloSign** | E-signatures | ~$10-25/mo/user |\n| **Mux** | Video hosting (academy) | $0.025/min stored + streaming |\n| **SendGrid/Postmark** | Transactional email | ~$20-80/mo |\n| **Firebase** | Push notifications, auth | Free tier generous |\n| **Algolia/Meilisearch** | Search | Free/self-hosted |\n| **BrightLocal API** | Citation management | ~$29-79/mo |\n| **DataForSEO** | Rank tracking, SERP data | ~$50-500/mo |\n| **CallRail API** | Call tracking alternative | ~$45-145/mo |\n\n---\n\n## PART 4: REVENUE MODEL\n\n### Revenue Streams\n\n1. **SaaS Subscriptions (Primary)**\n   - Starter: $149/mo (dispatch, driver app, billing, basic website)\n   - Growth: $299/mo (+ marketing suite, call tracking, AI assistant)\n   - Enterprise: $499/mo (+ broker marketplace, white-label, AI agents, academy)\n   - Custom: $799+/mo (multi-location, API access, custom development)\n\n2. **Payment Processing Spread**\n   - Charge 2.9% + 30¢, pay Stripe 2.9% + 30¢ = break even\n   - OR negotiate volume rates from Stripe → keep the spread\n   - ACH: charge 1%, pay ~0.5% = keep 0.5%\n\n3. **Broker Marketplace Fees**\n   - 10-20% commission on every brokered load\n   - At scale: 1,000 loads/month × $400 avg × 15% = $60K/month\n   - THIS is the massive revenue opportunity\n\n4. **Marketing Management Fees**\n   - Manage Google/Meta ads for haulers: 15-20% of ad spend\n   - Average hauler spends $2K-5K/mo on ads → $300-$1,000/mo revenue per hauler\n\n5. **AI Agent Usage Fees**\n   - AI phone agent: $0.50-$1.00/call answered\n   - AI chat agent: included in plan, premium features extra\n\n6. **Training Academy**\n   - Included in higher tiers\n   - Sell individual courses to non-subscribers: $49-$199/course\n\n7. **Data & Insights (Future)**\n   - Industry benchmark reports\n   - Market pricing data\n   - Hauler performance data (anonymized)\n\n### Revenue Projections (Conservative)\n- Year 1: 50 haulers × $299 avg = $179K ARR + $100K broker fees = ~$280K\n- Year 2: 200 haulers × $349 avg = $838K ARR + $400K broker/ads = ~$1.2M\n- Year 3: 500 haulers × $399 avg = $2.4M ARR + $1.2M broker/ads = ~$3.6M\n- Year 5: 2,000 haulers = $10M+ ARR (Docket-scale competitor)\n\n---\n\n## PART 5: DEVELOPMENT TIMELINE\n\n### Phase 1: MVP (Months 1-4) — $80K-$120K dev cost\n**Goal: Launch with core operations that match Docket + broker basics**\n- Order management, scheduling, dispatch\n- Driver mobile app (iOS + Android)\n- Asset tracking (GPS + QR)\n- Billing, invoicing, payments (Stripe)\n- Customer portal + online ordering\n- QuickBooks integration\n- Basic website builder\n- Text/email notifications\n- Basic broker tools (accept/assign brokered jobs)\n\n### Phase 2: Marketing Suite (Months 4-7) — $60K-$80K\n**Goal: The differentiator — what Docket can't do**\n- Call tracking + recording (Twilio)\n- AI call transcription (Whisper)\n- Google Ads management dashboard\n- SEO toolkit (rank tracking, audit, citations)\n- Review management + AI response drafting\n- Landing page builder\n- Meta Ads management\n\n### Phase 3: AI Agents (Months 7-10) — $50K-$70K\n**Goal: AI-powered automation that blows competitors away**\n- AI phone agent (24/7 call answering)\n- AI chat agent (website + SMS)\n- AI dispatch assistant\n- AI pricing engine\n- AI sales coaching from call analysis\n- Dynamic pricing by ZIP/demand\n\n### Phase 4: Marketplace & Academy (Months 10-14) — $60K-$80K\n**Goal: Build the network effect and broker engine**\n- Full 2-sided broker marketplace\n- Hauler onboarding and verification\n- Marketplace payments (Stripe Connect)\n- Training academy (LMS with video courses)\n- Multi-location/franchise support\n- White-label option\n\n### Phase 5: Scale & Intelligence (Months 14-18) — $40K-$60K\n**Goal: Data moat and national expansion**\n- National hauler database\n- Demand forecasting ML models\n- Competitor price monitoring\n- Advanced analytics and BI dashboards\n- Bing/YouTube ads management\n- Platform admin and tenant management tools\n\n### TOTAL ESTIMATED TIMELINE: 14-18 months to full platform\n### TOTAL ESTIMATED DEVELOPMENT COST: $290K-$410K\n\n*Note: These costs assume a mix of in-house development (your dev agents) + contracted specialized work. Using your AI dev agents significantly reduces cost — potentially 50-70% savings vs. traditional agency development.*\n\n---\n\n## PART 6: WHAT I NEED FROM YOU, JOSE\n\n1. **Business Entity:** Is this being built under USA Dumpster & Recycling, or a new entity? (General Counsel needs to know for IP, contracts, licensing)\n\n2. **Budget:** What's the initial development budget? This determines Phase 1 scope and whether we hire human contractors or build primarily with AI dev agents.\n\n3. **Domain/Brand Name:** What will the SaaS product be called? (Graphic Designer + CMO need this early)\n\n4. **Your Hauler Network:** How many hauler contacts do you currently have for the broker marketplace? This determines go-to-market for the marketplace side.\n\n5. **Current Tech Access:** Do you have AWS/GCP accounts, Stripe account, Twilio account, or should we set up fresh?\n\n6. **Existing Customer Data:** Can we export your current customer database to seed the CRM module?\n\n7. **Priority:** What's more important first — the operations software (Docket replacement for your own company) or the broker marketplace (to monetize other markets)?\n\n8. **Timeline Pressure:** Is there a deadline or event driving this (investor pitch, contract, competitor move)?\n\n---\n\n## PART 7: AGENT ASSIGNMENTS\n\nEach of your 32 agents has a role in this project:\n\n| Agent | Role in This Project |\n|-------|---------------------|\n| 👑 Master Agent | Project orchestrator, coordinates all agents |\n| 📋 Project Manager | Sprint planning, timeline, dependencies, milestone tracking |\n| 📊 McKinsey Consultant | Market sizing, viability study, competitive analysis, pricing strategy |\n| 🏦 Investment Banker | Funding strategy, investor deck, valuation modeling |\n| 🔧 CTO | Technology architecture, stack decisions, security, DevOps |\n| 🛠️ Route Optimizer Dev | Core dispatch + route optimization engine |\n| 💻 Software Dev | Platform development (web app, APIs, integrations) |\n| 🤖 AI / Data Scientist | ML models, AI agents, call transcription, demand forecasting |\n| 📈 CFO | Financial modeling, unit economics, burn rate, pricing |\n| 🧮 Accountant | Revenue tracking, payment processing setup, QuickBooks integration |\n| 🎯 CMO | Go-to-market strategy, content marketing, launch plan |\n| 📣 Paid Media Specialist | Google/Meta ads module design, PPC strategy for launch |\n| 🔍 SEO Agent | SEO module design, keyword strategy, content plan |\n| 📱 Social Media Manager | Launch campaign, brand building, community |\n| 📞 Sales Director | Hauler acquisition strategy, sales process, pricing |\n| 💬 Customer Service Manager | Customer support design, onboarding flows, help center |\n| 🎨 Graphic Designer | Brand identity, UI design, marketing assets |\n| 🎬 Video Editor | Training academy content, product demos, marketing videos |\n| ⚙️ COO | Operations module design, SOP templates, workflow design |\n| 🚛 Fleet Manager | Fleet module requirements, Samsara integration specs |\n| ⚖️📋 General Counsel | SaaS terms of service, privacy policy, IP protection, contracts |\n| 👷 CHRO | Training academy course design, HR compliance content |\n| 🦺 CSO | Safety training content for academy module |\n| 🏛️ Land Use Attorney | Compliance module for hauler permitting |\n| 🌿 Environmental Engineer | Environmental compliance content and tracking features |\n| ⚖️ Insurance Attorney | Insurance compliance tracking features |\n| 🛡️ Insurance Broker | Insurance marketplace opportunity assessment |\n| 🏠 Real Estate Agent | Market expansion analysis by geography |\n| 🏗️ Architect | Not directly involved (future: facility design module?) |\n| 🗺️ Civil Engineer | Not directly involved |\n| 👷‍♂️ Construction Manager | Not directly involved |\n| 📦 Procurement Manager | Technology vendor negotiation, API cost optimization |\n\n---\n\n## NEXT STEPS\n\n1. ✅ Master Plan complete (this document)\n2. ⏳ Jose answers the 8 questions in Part 6\n3. ⏳ McKinsey Consultant runs full market viability study\n4. ⏳ CTO produces detailed architecture document\n5. ⏳ Investment Banker builds financial model\n6. ⏳ Graphic Designer begins brand exploration\n7. ⏳ Project Manager creates Phase 1 sprint plan\n8. ⏳ Route Optimizer Dev + Software Dev begin MVP development\n\n---\n\n*This master plan is a living document. It will be updated as decisions are made and development progresses.*\n\n*Saved to: projects/saas-platform/MASTER-PLAN.md*\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":6169,"cacheRead":141364,"cacheWrite":304,"totalTokens":147838,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773800701400}}
