{"type":"message","id":"6dae8966","parentId":"b651d2ff","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:00:17.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"⚠️ *HEADS UP Jose — I'm at 84% context. I have enough for this update but the next major research/build task should be a fresh session to avoid hitting the limit.*\n\nHere's the domain check results:\n\n*🌐 BRAND NAME UPDATE:*\n\n- ❌ *HaulerHub.com* — TAKEN (freight marketplace)\n- ❌ *RollStack.com* — TAKEN (SaaS reporting tool)\n- ❌ *HaulCommand.com* — TAKEN (heavy haul marketplace)\n\n*✅ LIKELY AVAILABLE:*\n- *DumpRun.com* — domain not resolving (likely available to purchase!)\n- *HaulerOS.com* — domain not resolving (likely available!)\n- *RollOffIQ.com* — domain not resolving (likely available!)\n- *HaulerIQ.com* — page blank (may be parked, worth checking)\n- *HaulIQ.com* — page blank (may be parked, worth checking)\n\n*👉 MY TOP 3 PICKS NOW:*\n1. *HaulerIQ* — \"IQ\" signals intelligence/AI, speaks directly to haulers\n2. *DumpRun* — short, memorable, action-oriented, industry-native slang\n3. *HaulerOS* — \"Operating System for Haulers\" is a powerful positioning statement\n\nJose, pick your favorite (or tell me your own idea) and I'll verify domain availability + lock it in. Then in a *fresh session* I'll activate the full team to begin:\n\n1. General Counsel → FL LLC formation checklist\n2. CTO → detailed architecture document\n3. McKinsey Consultant → market viability study\n4. Graphic Designer → brand identity exploration\n5. Project Manager → Phase 1 sprint plan\n6. Route Optimizer Dev + Software Dev → begin MVP build\n\nEverything is saved in your workspace at `projects/saas-platform/MASTER-PLAN.md`. The team is ready to go 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":480,"cacheRead":156874,"cacheWrite":280,"totalTokens":157635,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773802802548}}
