{"type":"message","id":"3fff7610","parentId":"7be02676","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:04:18.810Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n*✅ LOCKED IN: HaulerIQ*\n\nLet me save all decisions to the master plan before this session wraps."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01RqhExuKFrEonYFCX3LfpFE","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace/projects/saas-platform/MASTER-PLAN.md","old_string":"# 🚀 MASTER PLAN: Roll-Off Waste Industry SaaS Platform\n## \"Docket Killer\" — Build, Operate, Broker, Dominate\n### Date: March 17, 2026\n### Prepared by: Master Agent (👑) — Coordinating ALL 32 Agents","new_string":"# 🚀 MASTER PLAN: HaulerIQ — Roll-Off Waste Industry SaaS Platform\n## Build, Operate, Broker, Dominate\n### Brand: HaulerIQ | Domain: hauleriq.com (TO PURCHASE)\n### Date: March 17, 2026\n### Prepared by: Master Agent (👑) — Coordinating ALL 32 Agents\n\n## LOCKED DECISIONS (March 17, 2026)\n1. **Entity:** New FL LLC (separate from USA Dumpster & Recycling)\n2. **Budget:** $25K-$75K (AI agents + 1-2 freelancers)\n3. **Brand:** HaulerIQ (hauleriq.com)\n4. **Hauler Network:** Begin building immediately\n5. **Tech Accounts:** Setup from scratch (full checklist needed)\n6. **Customer Data:** Export all existing data from USA Dumpster\n7. **Priority:** Operations + Broker marketplace together (MVP of both)\n8. **Timeline:** Build it right — MVP in 4 months (target: July 2026)\n9. **Context-Aware Routing:** AI analyzes ALL customer communications to feed route optimization"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":3,"output":508,"cacheRead":163546,"cacheWrite":602,"totalTokens":164659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773803044018}}
