{"type":"message","id":"85390070","parentId":"4f741d3b","timestamp":"2026-03-18T03:04:40.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01LCwdysrwbUv6kXxfQx7Yh7","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/josearango/.openclaw/master_workspace/memory/2026-03-17.md","content":"# March 17, 2026\n\n## Major Session — Agent Hiring + SaaS Master Plan\n\n### Agents Hired (32 total)\nBuilt out full 32-agent organization for Jose:\n- C-Suite: Master Agent, COO, CFO, CMO, CTO, General Counsel, CHRO, CSO\n- Advisory: McKinsey Consultant, Investment Banker\n- Legal: Land Use Attorney, Insurance Attorney\n- Operations: Fleet Manager, Environmental Engineer, Real Estate Agent\n- Engineering: Architect, Civil Engineer, Construction Manager, Route Optimizer Dev, Software Dev\n- Data: AI/Data Scientist\n- Sales/Customer: Sales Director, Customer Service Manager, Insurance Broker\n- Creative/Marketing: Graphic Designer, Video Editor, SEO Agent, Paid Media Specialist, Social Media Manager\n- Finance: Accountant\n- PM: Project Manager\n- Procurement: Procurement Manager\n\n### Alex Naranjo\n- Researched dump sites in Miami-Dade for his dumpster company\n- Gave him full list of county landfills, transfer stations, and private facilities\n\n### USA Dumpster & Recycling Audit\n- Completed full GBP + SEO + PMax audit\n- Saved to: audits/usa-dumpster-gbp-seo-pmax-audit.md\n- Key findings: business name inconsistency, dual domain problem, no LSA, needs GBP optimization\n- Website: usadumpsterrentals.net\n- Address: 3147 NW North River Dr, Suite #2, Miami, FL 33142\n\n### HaulerIQ — SaaS Platform Master Plan\n- Vision: Better version of Docket (yourdocket.com) with integrated SEO, ads, call tracking, AI agents, training academy, and broker marketplace\n- Brand name locked: HaulerIQ (hauleriq.com — needs to be purchased)\n- Entity: New FL LLC\n- Budget: $25K-$75K\n- Priority: Operations + Broker marketplace together\n- Timeline: MVP in 4 months (target July 2026)\n- Unique feature: Context-aware routing engine that analyzes all customer communications\n- Competitive intel: Docket has IronRouteAI, broker tools, SEO, website builder — but NO ads management, call tracking, AI agents, or training academy\n- Master plan saved to: projects/saas-platform/MASTER-PLAN.md\n\n### Competitive Intel Saved\n- Coastal Waste: TRUX (AMCS) + CurbWaste + WatchBot\n- Waste Management: Routeware + WM Smart Truck + Lytx + Fleetio\n- Docket: 3 tiers (Grow/Pro/Pro Plus), IronRouteAI, broker tools, review guard\n- Saved to route optimizer workspace: docs/competitive-intel/competitors.md\n\n### Next Steps (Next Session)\n1. Verify and purchase hauleriq.com domain\n2. General Counsel → FL LLC formation checklist\n3. CTO → detailed architecture document\n4. McKinsey Consultant → market viability study\n5. Graphic Designer → brand identity exploration\n6. Project Manager → Phase 1 sprint plan\n7. Route Optimizer Dev + Software Dev → begin MVP build\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"anthropic","model":"claude-opus-4-6","usage":{"input":1,"output":849,"cacheRead":164148,"cacheWrite":554,"totalTokens":165552,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773803058840}}
